%20been%20given.%20In%20three%20to%20four%20days%2C%20samples%20will%20be%20collected%20from%20all%20the%20spice%20manufacturing%20units%20of%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20top%20government%20sources%20have%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNot%20just%20MDH%20and%20Everest%2C%20samples%20will%20be%20taken%20from%20all%20the%20spice%20manufacturing%20companies.%20The%20report%20will%20come%20from%20the%20lab%20in%20about%2020%20days%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Hong%20Kong%2C%20Singapore%20Said%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Hong%20Kong%20and%20Singapore%20food%20regulators%20have%20warned%20people%20against%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fafter-singapore-hong-kong-bans-sale-of-mdh-everest-spices-5495187%5C%22%3E%20using%20four%20products%20from%20these%20two%20spice%20brands%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20the%20alleged%20presence%20of%20ethylene%20oxide%20at%20%26quot%3Blevels%20exceeding%20the%20permissible%20limit%26quot%3B.%20Ethylene%20oxide%20has%20been%20classified%20as%20a%20'Group%201%20carcinogen'%20by%20the%20International%20Agency%20for%20Research%20on%20Cancer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20spice%20products%20of%20MDH%20--%20Madras%20Curry%20Powder%20(spice%20blend%20for%20Madras%20Curry)%2C%20Sambhar%20Masala%20(Mixed%20Masala%20Powder)%2C%20and%20Curry%20Powder%20(Mixed%20Masala%20Powder)%20--%20along%20with%20Everest's%20Fish%20Curry%20Masala%20contain%20%E2%80%9Ca%20pesticide%2C%20ethylene%20oxide%26quot%3B%2C%20Hong%20Kong's%20Centre%20for%20Food%20Safety%20(CFS)%20said%20on%20April%205.%20The%20regulator%20instructed%20the%20vendors%20%E2%80%9Cto%20stop%20the%20sale%20and%20remove%20from%20shelves%20the%20affected%20products%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20Singapore%20Food%20Agency%20(SFA)%20also%20ordered%20a%20recall%20of%20Everest's%20Fish%20Curry%20Masala%20due%20to%20the%20presence%20of%20ethylene%20oxide%20at%20levels%20%E2%80%9Cexceeding%20the%20permissible%20limit%E2%80%9D.%20The%20SFA%20posted%20a%20release%20on%20its%20website%20on%20April%2018%20that%20said%20it%20%E2%80%9Chas%20directed%20the%20importer%2C%20Sp%20Muthiah%20%26amp%3B%20Sons%20Pte.%20Ltd.%2C%20to%20recall%20the%20products.%20The%20recall%20is%20ongoing.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20MDH%20and%20Everest%20Foods%20are%20yet%20to%20comment%20on%20these%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BStrict%20action%20will%20be%20taken%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20ban%20on%20using%20ethylene%20oxide%20in%20food%20items%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BStrict%20action%20will%20be%20taken%20if%20harmful%20substances%20are%20found%20in%20Indian%20spices.%20There%20is%20a%20provision%20for%20criminal%20proceedings%20also%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20has%20appealed%20to%20the%20Spices%20Board%2C%20under%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Commerce%20and%20Industry%2C%20to%20spread%20awareness%20that%20no%20harmful%20elements%20should%20be%20added%20to%20the%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20board%20has%20said%20it%20was%20looking%20into%20the%20ban%20imposed%20by%20Hong%20Kong%20and%20Singapore%20on%20the%20sale%20of%20four%20spices-mix%20products%20of%20Indian%20brands.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20looking%20into%20the%20matter.%20We%20are%20at%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Spices%20Board%20of%20India%20Director%20AB%20Rema%20Shree%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sources%20insisted%20that%20they%20had%20been%20testing%20samples%20even%20before%20the%20incidents%20in%20Hong%20Kong%20and%20Singapore%20and%20claimed%2C%20%26quot%3BSo%20far%2C%20no%20harmful%20elements%20have%20been%20found%20in%20the%20spices%20of%20different%20brands%20available%20in%20the%20Indian%20market%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20continuous%20process%20of%20sampling.%20This%20time%20we%20will%20take%20samples%20more%20quickly%20and%20in%20greater%20numbers%20than%20whatever%20samples%20we%20were%20taking%20earlier%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20ethylene%20oxide%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Spices%20Board%20defines%20ethylene%20oxide%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bflammable%2C%20colourless%20gas%20at%20temperatures%20above%2010.7%20Celsius.%20It%20serves%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bdisinfectant%2C%20fumigant%2C%20sterilising%20agent%20and%20insecticide%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20mainly%20used%20to%20sterilise%20medical%20equipment%20and%20to%20reduce%20microbial%20contamination%20in%20spices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20being%20produced%20from%20natural%20sources%2C%20it%20can%20also%20be%20generated%20from%20water-logged%20soil%2C%20manure%2C%20and%20sewage%20sludge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEthylene%20oxide's%20health%20effects%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20World%20Health%20Organization's%20International%20Agency%20for%20Research%20on%20Cancer%20(IARC)%20classifies%20ethylene%20oxide%20as%20a%20'Group%201%20carcinogen'%2C%20meaning%20it%20has%20%26quot%3Benough%20evidence%20to%20conclude%20that%20it%20can%20cause%20cancer%20in%20humans%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShort-term%20exposure%20to%20the%20carcinogen%20can%20affect%20the%20human%20central%20nervous%20system%2C%20and%20cause%20depression%20and%20irritation%20of%20the%20eyes%20and%20mucous%20membranes%20but%20prolonged%20exposure%20can%20irritate%20the%20eyes%2C%20skin%2C%20nose%2C%20throat%2C%20and%20lungs%2C%20and%20damage%20the%20brain%20and%20nervous%20system%2C%20as%20per%20the%20US%20Environmental%20Protection%20Agency%20(EPA).%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713791160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fbtqj1nk8_mdh-everest-masala-_625x300_22_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-to-test-samples-after-indian-spice-brands-banned-in-hong-kong-singapore-5497633%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20government%20has%20ordered%20food%20commissioners%20to%20collect%20samples%20of%20spices%20from%20all%20the%20manufacturing%20units%20in%20the%20country%2C%20sources%20said%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-to-test-samples-after-indian-spice-brands-banned-in-hong-kong-singapore-5497633%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-to-test-samples-after-indian-spice-brands-banned-in-hong-kong-singapore-5497633%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-to-test-samples-after-indian-spice-brands-banned-in-hong-kong-singapore-5497633%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UN%20chief%20accepts%20independent%20review%20of%20UNRWA%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713790956000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-109505653%2Cimgsize-792347.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fun-chief-accepts-independent-review-of-unrwa%2Farticleshow%2F109505536.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F109505536.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fun-chief-accepts-independent-review-of-unrwa%2Farticleshow%2F109505536.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fun-chief-accepts-independent-review-of-unrwa%2Famp_articleshow%2F109505536.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fun-chief-accepts-independent-review-of-unrwa%2Famp_articleshow%2F109505536.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I'm%20a%20tax%20lawyer%20who%20helps%20wealthy%20people%20move%20to%20lower%20their%20taxes%20%E2%80%94%20and%20prepare%20for%20residency%20audits%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20headshot%20of%20a%20man%20on%20the%20left%2C%20and%20an%20aerial%20shot%20of%20New%20York%20City%20on%20the%20right%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F662287d220b15f0ff4299133%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EHodgson%20Russ%20LLP%3B%20Alexander%20Spatari%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAs%20a%20tax%20lawyer%2C%20Mark%20Klein%2C%20has%20seen%20wealthy%20individuals%20continue%20to%20relocate%20to%20tax-free%20states.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWhile%20savings%20are%20the%20main%20reason%2C%20cultural%20fit%20also%20plays%20a%20role%20in%20relocation.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EFor%20movers%2C%20it%20isn't%20as%20simple%20as%20picking%20up%20a%20driver%20license%20%E2%80%94%20you%20must%20prove%20that%20you%20live%20there.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20partner%20and%20chairman%20emeritus%20at%20Hodgson%20Russ%20LLP%2C%20Mark%20Klein%2C%20who%20specializes%20in%20tax%20law.%20The%20conversation%20was%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20a%20tax%20lawyer%20who%20specializes%20in%20residency%20issues%2C%20and%20half%20of%20my%20job%20is%20helping%20people%20move%20to%20other%20states%20without%20triggering%20all%20sorts%20of%20nasty%20taxes%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhere-rich-people-are-moving-florida-texas-tennessee-north-carolina-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eand%2C%20in%20other%20cases%2C%20avoiding%20high%20taxes%20and%20going%20to%20low-tax%20states.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20people%20realize%20they%20have%20this%20greater%20flexibility%2C%20and%20if%20all%20other%20things%20are%20equal%2C%20why%20not%20save%20a%20bunch%20of%20money%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20my%20clients%20don't%20just%20put%20the%20money%20in%20their%20pocket.%20They%20use%20it%20for%20good%20things%2C%20they%20use%20it%20for%20charitable%20means%20that%20are%20important%20to%20them%2C%20and%20they%20just%20don't%20like%20what%20the%20government%20seems%20to%20be%20doing%20with%20the%20money%2C%20so%20it%20makes%20sense%20for%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20reasons%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpandemic-prompts-wall-street-to-look-south-for-floridas-life-and-work-benefits-2020-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFlorida%20real%20estate%20market%20was%20booming%20after%20Covid%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20because%20people%20realized%20that%20they%20could%20work%20just%20as%20effectively%20from%20anywhere.%20You%20didn't%20need%20to%20go%20to%20the%20office%20when%20you%20could%20do%20just%20as%20well%20with%20a%20computer%20and%20a%20telephone.%20And%20so%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20moved%20to%20Florida.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinance%20is%20big%2C%20but%20consulting%20services%20are%20as%20well.%20If%20you're%20a%20consultant%2C%20you%20just%20need%20to%20be%20where%20a%20telephone%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20thought%20we'd%20seen%20the%20bulk%20of%20the%20moving%20as%20a%20result%20right%20after%20Covid%2C%20but%20no%3A%20it%20seems%20to%20have%20continued%20unabated.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20we're%20seeing%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20who%20are%20enjoying%20liquidity%20events.%20They're%20about%20to%20sell%20their%20business%20that%20they've%20been%20working%20at%20forever.%20New%20York%20City%2C%20depending%20on%20your%20income%2C%20you%20could%20pay%2015%25%20tax%20on%20whatever%20it%20is%20you%20make%2C%20so%20you%20sell%20your%20business%20for%20%24100%20million%2C%20which%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20money%2C%20but%20still%20%2415%20million%20goes%20just%20from%20taxes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20feel%20that%20they%20could%20do%20a%20lot%20better%20with%20%2415%20million%20than%20the%20government.%20I%20think%20that's%20one%20of%20the%20reasons%20that%20we're%20seeing%20a%20continued%20push%20for%20people%20moving%20to%20places%20like%20Florida%20or%20Nevada%20or%20Texas%20or%20wherever.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20more%20income%20you%20have%2C%20the%20more%20flexibility%20you%20have.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ESaving%20money%20is%20a%20large%20factor%2C%20but%20not%20the%20only%20one%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20my%20clients%20are%20billionaires%20with%20a%20capital%20B%2C%20and%20they%20have%20tremendous%20sources%20of%20income%20that%20would%20not%20be%20taxed%20by%20a%20state%20like%20New%20York%20if%20they%20were%20simply%20a%20Floridian.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20can%20continue%20to%20come%20back%20to%20New%20York%20now%20and%20then%20and%20they%20can%20keep%20a%20place%20in%20New%20York.%20Some%20of%20them%20even%20have%20their%20own%20planes%2C%20so%20they%20don't%20worry%20too%20much%20about%20getting%20in%20line%20at%20TSA.%20They%20can%20go%20where%20they%20want%20to%20go%20when%20they%20want%20to%20go%2C%20and%20it%20does%20save%20them%20a%20lot%20of%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20clients%20are%20all%20over%20the%20country.%20I%20think%20Nevada%20has%20become%20very%20popular%2C%20especially%20the%20Lake%20Tahoe%20area%20for%20people%20who%20were%20in%20Los%20Angeles%20or%20the%20Silicon%20Valley%20area.%20You%20can%20live%20on%20one%20side%20of%20Lake%20Tahoe%20and%20pay%20no%20taxes%20versus%20the%20other%20side%20of%20Lake%20Tahoe%20and%20pay%20California%20taxes%2C%20which%20is%20around%2012%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20seeing%20people%20move%20to%20Wyoming%2C%20of%20all%20places%20because%20there%20are%20no%20taxes.%20And%20people%20absolutely%20love%20nature%20and%20their%20ability%20to%20commune%20with%20wild%20animals.%20That%20seems%20to%20be%20popular.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20people%20are%20even%20moving%20up%20to%20Washington%20state%2C%20which%20really%20doesn't%20tax%20you%20unless%20you%20are%20a%20gazillionaire.%20It%20depends%20on%20where%20your%20interests%20lie.%20Some%20people%20are%20into%20nature%2C%20and%20so%20Wyoming%20would%20be%20perfect.%20Some%20people%20are%20into%20the%20Miami%20scene.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENew%20York%20to%20Florida%20is%20still%20the%20most%20popular%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20to%20the%20east%20coast%20of%20Florida.%20We%20find%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20from%20New%20York%20City%20and%20Long%20Island%20find%20that%20the%20culture%20is%20kind%20of%20the%20same%20on%20the%20East%20Coast%2C%20whether%20it's%20Palm%20Beach%20or%20Boca%20or%20Delray%20or%20Miami.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EClearly%2C%20Florida%20has%20a%20tremendous%20attraction%20in%20the%20winter%2C%20given%20that%20you%20can%20leave%20Florida%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20summer%20and%20hurricane%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20with%20means%20absolutely%20find%20themselves%20going%20to%20Florida%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20think%20it's%20just%20for%20the%20money.%20I%20think%20also%20it's%20a%20better%20way%20of%20life.%20They%20can%20drive%20to%20the%20grocery%20store%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20winter%20and%20not%20worry%20about%20icy%20roads.%20But%20certainly%20saving%2015%25%20is%20kind%20of%20gravy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EIn%20order%20to%20avoid%20an%20audit%2C%20you%20need%20more%20than%20just%20paperwork%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20lot%20of%20people%20don't%20understand%20the%20rules.%20The%20very%20common%20misconception%20is%20that%20if%20I%20go%20to%20Florida%20and%20I%20spend%20183%20plus%20one%20days%2C%20I'm%20a%20Floridian.%20And%20nothing%20could%20be%20further%20from%20the%20truth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20law%20says%20you%20have%20to%20move%20to%20a%20place%20like%20Florida%2C%20and%20you%20have%20to%20prove%20that%20you%20did%20it%20by%20clear%20and%20convincing%20evidence.%20Now%2C%20I%20don't%20know%20what%20that%20means%2C%20but%20I%20know%20what%20it%20doesn't%20mean.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20in%20New%20York%20for%20six%20months%20and%20in%20Florida%20for%20six%20months%2C%20that's%20not%20clear%20and%20convincing.%20That's%20anything%20but.%20The%20other%20misconception%20is%20that%20people%20think%20that%20if%20they%20go%20to%20a%20place%20like%20Florida%2C%20they%20fill%20out%20an%20affidavit%20of%20domicile%2C%20they%20register%20to%20vote%2C%20they%20get%20the%20homestead%20exemption%20and%20a%20driver's%20license%2C%20somehow%20the%20residency%20fairy%20will%20tap%20them%20on%20the%20shoulder%20and%20make%20them%20a%20Floridian.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShould%20you%20do%20those%20things%3F%20Sure.%20But%20states%20don't%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20respect%20for%20paperwork.%20If%20I%20went%20to%20Florida%20right%20now%20and%20filled%20out%20a%20bunch%20of%20paperwork%2C%20does%20that%20make%20me%20a%20Floridian%3F%20No.%20It%20just%20means%20I'm%20really%20good%20at%20papers.%20It's%20the%20way%20you%20live%20your%20life.%20People%20who%20want%20this%20to%20work%20have%20to%20be%20willing%20to%20change%20the%20way%20they%20live%20their%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGod%20forbid%20you're%20ill%20and%20you%20come%20back%20to%20the%20Tri-state%20area%20for%20medical%20care%2C%20that's%20okay.%20We%20expect%20people%20are%20going%20to%20look%20for%20the%20best%20medical%20care%20they%20can.%20But%20if%20you%20need%20to%20go%20to%20the%20dentist%20to%20get%20your%20teeth%20cleaned%2C%20shouldn't%20you%20go%20to%20a%20dentist%20near%20your%20home%3F%20It's%20very%20unusual%20for%20people%20to%20travel%201%2C500%20miles%20north%20just%20to%20get%20their%20teeth%20cleaned.%20It's%20the%20kind%20of%20thing%20you%20do%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20even%20better%20indicator%20is%2C%20tell%20me%20where%20your%20spouse%20is.%20Most%20spouses%20wait%20at%20home%20when%20the%20other%20spouse%20needs%20to%20travel%20for%20business.%20Tell%20me%20where%20your%20dog%20is%20located.%20Who%20keeps%20their%20dog%20with%20them%20when%20they%20commute%20to%20work%20or%20when%20they're%20on%20vacation%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhere%20do%20you%20sleep%20at%20night%3F%20There%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20here%20in%20Manhattan%20who%20don't%20pay%20a%20penny%20of%20New%20York%20City%20income%20tax%2C%20even%20though%20they're%20here%20every%20day%20and%20their%20job%20is%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20look%20at%20what%20they%20call%20the%20%26quot%3Bnear%20and%20dear%20test%2C%26quot%3B%20where%20are%20things%20that%20are%20important%20to%20you%20located%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20assumption%20is%20that%20most%20people%20have%20their%20good%20stuff%20%E2%80%94%20their%20nicest%20stuff%20%E2%80%94%20in%20their%20homes.%20It's%20going%20to%20really%20look%20weird%20if%20you%20don't%20claim%20to%20be%20a%20New%20Yorker%2C%20but%20you've%20got%20a%20%245%20million%20piece%20of%20artwork%20on%20the%20wall%2C%20and%20your%20Peloton%20is%20here%2C%20and%20your%20best%20golf%20clubs%20and%20your%20Steinway%20piano%2C%20or%20whatever%20the%20heck%20you're%20into%2C%20are%20in%20New%20York.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAuditors%20look%20at%20that%2C%20too.%20We%20always%20tell%20people%20that%20being%20audited%20for%20residency%20is%20kind%20of%20like%20the%20tax%20version%20of%20a%20colonoscopy.%20It's%20very%20intrusive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20political%20climate%20is%20not%20really%20favorable%20for%20the%20super-wealthy%2C%20and%20they%20feel%20kind%20of%20put%20upon.%20Here%20in%20New%20York%20City%2C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcomptroller.nyc.gov%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fdocuments%2FSpotlight_PIT-Taxpayers.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20the%20top%201%25%20of%20the%20taxpayers%20pay%20almost%2050%25%20of%20the%20New%20York%20City%20income%20tax%3C%2Fa%3E.%20One%20percent%20pays%2050%25.%20The%20idea%20that%20my%20clients%20are%20told%20in%20the%20press%20that%20they're%20not%20paying%20their%20fair%20share%20and%20that%20we%20should%20increase%20taxes%20on%20them%20doesn't%20sit%20well%20with%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20feel%20that%20they're%20doing%20their%20fair%20share%2C%20they're%20paying%20more%20than%20their%20fair%20share