everal%20awareness%20campaigns%20run%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Felection-commission-holds-meeting-to-mitigate-risks-due-to-heatwave-5497221%5C%22%3EElection%20Commission%20of%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20NGOs%2C%20influencers%2C%20and%20the%20media%2C%20which%20usually%20result%20in%20an%20organic%20increase%20in%20vote%20share%20by%201-1.5%25.%20In%20today's%20world%2C%20where%20social%20media%20plays%20a%20pivotal%20role%20in%20shaping%20opinions%2C%20it%20is%20difficult%20to%20overlook%20these%20campaigns%20and%20their%20impact.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Led%20To%20Low%20Turnout%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20factors%20could%20account%20for%20this%20drop%20in%20turnout.%20Heat%20waves%20are%20being%20cited%20as%20one%20of%20the%20primary%20reasons.%20For%20instance%2C%20in%20Muzaffarnagar%2C%20the%20temperature%20at%20noon%20on%20April%2019%2C%20the%20day%20of%20voting%2C%20was%2033oC%2C%20compared%20to%20around%2029oC%20five%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20possible%20that%20the%20rhetoric%20around%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party's%20(BJP)%20'Mission%20400'%20and%20slogans%20like%20%26quot%3BAayega%20to%20Modi%20Hi%26quot%3B%20instilled%20some%20complacency%20among%20BJP%20supporters.%20Conversely%2C%20it%20could%20also%20be%20that%20a%20lack%20of%20enthusiasm%20among%20opposition%20supporters%2C%20who%20might%20perceive%20these%20elections%20as%20a%20foregone%20conclusion%20now%2C%20kept%20people%20away%20from%20polling%20booths.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Rajasthan%20and%20western%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20emergence%20of%20caste%20and%20community%20issues%20may%20also%20have%20contributed%20to%20the%20low%20turnout%20numbers.%20Dissatisfaction%20within%20the%20Rajput%20community%20over%20Union%20minister%20Pursushottam%20Rupala's%20statement%20and%20demands%20for%20the%20withdrawal%20of%20his%20candidature%2C%20coupled%20with%20discontent%20within%20the%20Jat%20community%20due%20to%20the%20farmers'%20unrest%2C%20may%20have%20affected%20voting%20in%20these%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20absence%20of%20remote%20polling%20mechanisms%20may%20have%20made%20it%20difficult%20for%20migrant%20populations%20in%20states%20like%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20Maharashtra%20to%20return%20to%20their%20home%20states%20to%20cast%20their%20votes%2C%20thus%20impacting%20voting%20in%20Bihar%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20Rajasthan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EYouth%20And%20Politics%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20notable%20is%20the%20fact%20that%20only%2038%25%20of%20young%20eligible%20voters%20chose%20to%20register%20themselves%20speaks%20about%20the%20disconnect%20young%20people%20feel%20with%20contemporary%20politics%20and%20politicians.%20Politics%20is%20often%20perceived%20as%20a%20dirty%20word%20among%20youngsters%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20low%20turnout%20in%20urban%20centres%20like%20Chennai%20highlights%20significant%20urban%20apathy.%20Various%20parties%2C%20including%20the%20DMK%20and%20the%20AIADMK%2C%20have%20led%20governments%20in%20the%20state%20over%20the%20years.%20But%20none%20has%20been%20able%20to%20address%20issues%20like%20waterlogging%20and%20floods%20during%20monsoon.%20This%20casts%20doubts%20about%20the%20political%20will%20of%20these%20parties%20as%20well%20as%20the%20capabilities%20of%20their%20leaders%20and%20the%20bureaucracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20increasingly%20polarised%20nature%20of%20elections%2C%20marked%20by%20shrill%20campaigns%20from%20political%20parties%2C%20is%20also%20alienating%20a%20section%20of%20voters%20from%20the%20political%20process.%20In%20a%20landscape%20divided%20between%20pro-government%20and%20anti-government%20factions%2C%20there's%20little%20space%20for%20neutral%20voters.%20Moreover%2C%20none%20of%20the%20political%20parties%20has%20active%20apolitical%20community%20outreach%20programmes%2C%20and%20there's%20a%20lack%20of%20mechanisms%20for%20active%20public%20participation%20in%20governance%2C%20even%20at%20the%20local%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EVoter%20Disconnect%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere's%20a%20growing%20sense%20of%20frustration%20among%20voters%20as%20politicians%20prioritise%20rhetoric%20over%20addressing%20real%20issues%20affecting%20the%20common%20man.%20The%20repetition%20of%20the%20same%20speeches%20by%20the%20top%20leadership%20across%20parties%20has%20only%20exacerbated%20this%20feeling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReports%20indicate%20that%20this%20election%20has%20also%20seen%20a%20reduction%20in%20ground-level%20campaigning%20activities%20like%20door-to-door%20visits%2C%20small%20meetings%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3Enukkad%20sabhas%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20could%20possibly%20be%20contributing%20to%20voter%20disengagement.%20Social%20media%20discussions%20also%20point%20to%20an%20apparent%20disillusionment%20of%20the%20middle%20class%2C%20which%20feels%20that%20it%20pays%20significant%20taxes%20but%20receives%20inadequate%20benefits%20in%20return%2C%20including%20no%20access%20to%20social%20security%20or%20coverage%20under%20schemes%20like%20Ayushman%20Bharat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20time%20for%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%2C%20political%20parties%2C%20and%20leaders%20to%20reassess%20their%20strategies%20and%20re-engage%20voters%20in%20the%20remaining%20six%20phases%20of%20the%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Amitabh%20Tiwari%20is%20a%20political%20strategist%20and%20commentator.%20In%20his%20earlier%20avatar%2C%20he%20was%20a%20corporate%20and%20investment%20banker.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713789900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2017-02%2Fvoting-generic_650x400_81488189947.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Flok-sabha-elections-turnout-is-polarisation-pushing-peopl