nsider.com%2Fsoda-around-the-world-2019-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esoda%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fsoda-around-the-world-2019-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eflavors%3C%2Fa%3E%20I%20could%20find.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEach%2012-ounce%20can%20of%20soda%20contains%20under%2025%20calories%2C%20which%20is%20significantly%20less%20than%20what%20you'd%20find%20in%20the%20same-size%20serving%20of%20Coke%20or%20Fanta.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrying-every-flavor-dannon-light-fit-yogurt-ranking%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eranking%20of%20the%20flavors%20I%20tried%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20from%20worst%20to%20best.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWatermelon%20was%20easily%20my%20least%20favorite%20flavor.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22845%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20open%20can%20of%20watermelon%20Poppi%20next%20to%20a%20small%2C%20clear%20glass%20with%20pink%20liquid%20inside.%20Both%20are%20sitting%20on%20a%20countertop.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F662036e810c6b0cde5f08256%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22633%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20found%20that%20Poppi's%20watermelon%20flavor%20tasted%20medicinal.%20%3Cp%3ETed%20Berg%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlthough%20it%20wasn't%20easy%20picking%20my%20favorite%20Poppi%20flavor%2C%20I%20had%20no%20trouble%20selecting%20my%20least%20favorite.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20typically%20enjoy%20watermelon-flavored%20things%20(it's%20my%20go-to%20Blow%20Pop%20flavor%2C%20for%20example)%2C%20but%20Poppi's%20effort%20at%20it%20tasted%20medicinal%20to%20me.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20thought%20it%20tasted%20like%20the%20watermelon-flavored%20toothpaste%20that%20hung%20around%20in%20our%20medicine%20cabinet%20for%20months%20after%20my%20kids%20rejected%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20was%20disappointed%20by%20the%20strawberry-lemon%20flavor.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221332%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20can%20of%20strawberry-lemon%20Poppi%20on%20a%20countertop.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6622afa983c8ec6e15302c4b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22999%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20could%20make%20out%20the%20distinct%20tastes%20of%20both%20strawberry%20and%20lemon.%3Cp%3ETed%20Berg%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EStrawberry%20lemon%20sounded%20like%20a%20great%20idea%20for%20a%20soda%20flavor.%20When%20I%20took%20a%20sip%2C%20I%20could%20taste%20the%20distinct%20flavors%20of%20both%20strawberry%20and%20lemon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20something%20about%20this%20flavor%20tasted%20too%20artificial%20to%20me%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20in%20the%20aftertaste.%20It%20reminded%20me%20of%20the%20bubblegum%20that%20used%20to%20come%20with%20packs%20of%20baseball%20cards.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERaspberry%20rose%20was%20too%20floral%20for%20me.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22881%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20open%20can%20of%20raspberry%20rose%20Poppi%20next%20to%20a%20small%2C%20clear%20glass%20with%20pink%20liquid%20inside.%20Both%20are%20sitting%20on%20a%20countertop.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66212f3e49058e6693573bf5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22661%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20didn't%20love%20Poppi's%20raspberry-rose%20flavor.%3Cp%3ETed%20Berg%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20found%20many%20of%20Poppi's%20most%20creative%20flavors%20to%20be%20disappointing%2C%20and%20raspberry%20rose%20was%20no%20exception.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20had%20a%20nice%2C%20crisp%20raspberry%20flavor%2C%20but%20it%20was%20overwhelmed%20by%20a%20perfumy%20floral%20taste%20that%20became%20increasingly%20unpleasant%20as%20I%20drank%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wouldn't%20be%20surprised%20if%20someone%20handed%20me%20something%20that%20tasted%20just%20like%20this%20at%20the%20cocktail%20hour%20of%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwedding-planning-mistakes-couples-make-according-to-photographer-2021-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eoutdoor%20wedding%3C%2Fa%3E.%20However%2C%20I'd%20probably%20only%20take%20a%20few%20sips%20before%20ditching%20it%20on%20an%20empty%20table%20somewhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EPoppi's%20root-beer%20flavor%20was%20fine%20%E2%80%94%20but%20I'd%20prefer%20the%20traditional%20version.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221369%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20unopened%20can%20of%20Poppi%20root%20beer%20on%20a%20countertop.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6622aefd83c8ec6e15302bf7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221027%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20thought%20Poppi's%20root%20beer%20had%20a%20yeasty%20aftertaste.%3Cp%3ETed%20Berg%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPoppi's%20root%20beer%20was%20sweet%20and%20rich%20and%20had%20a%20familiar%20root-beer%20flavor.%20However%2C%20it%20lacked%20the%20spicy%20bite%20of%20the%20best%20root%20beers%2C%20and%20there%20was%20something%20almost%20yeasty%20in%20the%20aftertaste%2C%20which%20I%20thought%20was%20a%20little%20strange.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20floated%20ice%20cream%20in%20worse%2C%20but%20I%20wouldn't%20choose%20this%20over%20a%20traditional%20root%20beer%20(or%20even%20its%20diet%20equivalent).%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20grape-flavored%20Poppi%20was%20slightly%20tart.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22915%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20open%20can%20of%20grape%20Poppi%20next%20to%20a%20small%2C%20clear%20glass%20with%20dark-purple%20liquid%20inside.%20Both%20are%20sitting%20on%20a%20countertop.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6621318a49058e6693573d3a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22686%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20hadn't%20had%20a%20grape%20soda%20in%20decades.%3Cp%3ETed%20Berg%3C%2Fp%3E%3