%26quot%3B%20Remark%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20approached%20the%20Election%20Commission%20demanding%20action%20over%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20claim%20that%20the%20party%2C%20if%20brought%20to%20power%2C%20will%20redistribute%20the%20nation's%20wealth%20in%20favour%20of%20Muslims%20and%20is%20also%20eyeing%20women's%20%26quot%3Bmangalsutras%26quot%3B%20for%20this%20cause.%20The%20party%20has%20already%20vehemently%20criticised%20PM%20Modi%2C%20accusing%20him%20of%20making%20%26quot%3Bdivisive%20comments%26quot%3B.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIts%20letter%20to%20Commission%20contained%20its%20strongest%20remarks%20in%20recent%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20we%20have%20objections%20to%20the%20entire%20tone%20and%20tenor%20of%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%20speech%2C%20in%20this%20representation%20we%20wish%20to%20highlight%20the%20completely%20unprecedented%20and%20malicious%20allegations%20as%20well%20statements%20which%20are%20clearly%20aimed%20at%20creating%20enmity%20between%20groups%2C%20far%20worse%20than%20any%20ever%20made%20by%20a%20sitting%20Prime%20Minister%20in%20the%20history%20of%20India.%20This%20cannot%20go%20unchecked%2C%20unanswered%20and%20unpunished%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20letter%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20also%20said%20the%20PM%20Modi%20and%20the%20BJP's%20repeated%20comments%20invoking%20religious%20sentiments%20%26quot%3Bhas%20been%20bolstered%20by%20the%20Hon'ble%20Commission's%20inaction%26quot%3B%20in%20penalising%20them%20for%20their%20%26quot%3Bblatant%20and%20direct%20violations%20of%20electoral%20laws%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20PM%20had%20given%20a%20speech%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20which%20targets%20a%20particular%20community%20which%20may%20snatch%20our%20national%20resources.%20That%20community%20is%20linked%20with%20infiltrators.%20His%20allegations%20about%20an%20attack%20on%20Mangalsutras%2C%20is%20again%20a%20religious%20link.%C2%A0%20It%20is%20a%20blatant%20violation%20of%20ECI%20circular%2C%26quot%3B%20senior%20party%20leader%20Abhishek%20Manu%20Singhvi%20said%20after%20meeting%20the%20Commission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20thankful%20to%20ECI%20to%20give%20us%20time%2C%20we%20had%20raised%2017%20issues%20which%20attacks%20the%20basic%20principles%20of%20our%20constitution%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20had%20first%20raised%20the%20issue%20in%20Rajasthan%20over%20the%20weekend%20and%20then%20reiterated%20in%20western%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20where%20elections%20are%20due%20later%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20manifesto%2C%20he%20said%2C%20promises%20that%20if%20they%20come%20to%20power%2C%20%26quot%3Beveryone's%20property%20will%20be%20surveyed%2C%20it%20will%20calculate%20gold%20belonging%20to%20mothers%20and%20sisters%20and%20then%20redistribute%20it.%20They%20won't%20even%20spare%20your%20mangalsutra%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20when%20the%20Congress%20was%20in%20power%20under%20Dr%20Manmohan%20Singh%2C%20it%20had%20said%20Muslims%20have%20the%20first%20right%20on%20the%20country's%20wealth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20means%20that%20they%20will%20gather%20this%20property%20and%20distribute%20it%20among%20people%20who%20have%20more%20children%2C%20among%20infiltrators.%20Will%20your%20hard-earned%20money%20be%20given%20to%20infiltrators%3F%20Do%20you%20accept%20this%3F%20The%20Congress%20manifesto%20is%20saying%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713788460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fh0piqe6g_narendra-modi_625x300_21_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmust-act-congress-to-election-commission-over-pms-wealth-to-infiltrators-remark-5497957%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Congress%20has%20approached%20the%20Election%20Commission%20demanding%20action%20against%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20c