blank%5C%22%3Ecolon%20cancer%20in%20people%20under%2055%20%3C%2Fa%3Ehave%20steadily%20risen%20by%20around%202%25%20a%20year%2C%20according%20to%20the%20American%20Cancer%20Society.%20It%20is%20now%20the%20deadliest%20cancer%20for%20men%20under%2050%20in%20the%20US%2C%20and%20the%20second%20deadliest%20for%20women%20the%20same%20age.%20In%202020%2C%20around%20%2424.3%20billion%20was%20spent%20on%20treating%20colorectal%20cancer%2C%20accounting%20for%2012.6%25%20of%20all%20US%20cancer%20treatment%20costs%2C%20according%20to%20the%20ACS.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlcohol%2C%20a%20lack%20of%20physical%20activity%2C%20and%20eating%20a%20traditional%20Western%20diet%20can%20all%20increase%20colon%20cancer%20risk%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thecancerdietitian.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMeredy%20Birdi%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20cancer%20dietitian%20based%20in%20London%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20This%20means%20a%20diet%20high%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feating-ultra-processed-foods-ovarian-brain-cancer-risk-2022-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eultra-processed%20foods%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20refined%20carbohydrates%20such%20as%20white%20bread%2C%20pizza%2C%20and%20cookies%2C%20and%20saturated%20fats%20found%20in%20fatty%20meats%20and%20butter%2C%20that's%20also%20lacking%20in%20fiber%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFiber%20comes%20from%20plants%20such%20as%20whole%20grains%2C%20fruits%20and%20vegetables%2C%20legumes%2C%20nuts%2C%20and%20seeds%2C%20and%20there's%20strong%20evidence%20to%20suggest%20that%20it%20lowers%20colon%20cancer%20risk.%20It%20feeds%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fboost-improve-gut-health-simple-effective-methods-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egood%20bacteria%20in%20the%20gut%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Birdi%20said%2C%20which%20protect%20the%20gut%20lining.%20It%20also%20acts%20as%20nature's%20broom%2C%20sweeping%20out%20toxins%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBirdi%20said%20that%20people%20should%20aim%20to%20eat%20plant-based%2075%25%20of%20the%20time.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20about%20balance.%20So%20nobody%20needs%20to%20worry%20about%20the%20occasional%20things%20that%20they%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20shared%20three%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhigh-fiber-recipes-to-help-hit-recommended-daily-target-2021-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efiber-filled%20dinner%20recipes%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20could%20help%20prevent%20colon%20cancer%20with%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EBean%20chili%20with%20brown%20rice%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbeans-could-be-secret-for-living-longer-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBeans%20are%20an%20excellent%20source%20of%20fiber%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20well%20as%20plant-based%20protein.%20They're%20a%20good%20substitute%20for%20red%20meat%2C%20which%20has%20been%20linked%20to%20an%20increased%20risk%20of%20colon%20cancer%2C%20according%20to%20the%20World%20Cancer%20Research%20Fund%20International%2C%20a%20cancer-prevention%20organization%20focused%20on%20how%20diet%2C%20weight%2C%20and%20physical%20activity%20can%20affect%20cancer%20survival%20rates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20bean%20chili%20with%20vegetables%20and%20brown%20rice%20is%20a%20simple%2C%20high-fiber%20dinner%20that%20contains%20legumes%2C%20whole%20grains%2C%20and%20vegetables%2C%20Birdi%20said.%20She%20recommended%20this%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wcrf-uk.org%2Frecipe%2Fbean-chilli%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecipe%3C%2Fa%3E%20shared%20by%20the%20WCRF%2C%20but%20specified%20that%20it's%20best%20to%20use%20olive%20oil%2C%20a%20source%20of%20healthy%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fdiet-nutrition%2Fsaturated-vs-unsaturated-fat%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20unsaturated%20fats%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20takes%2025%20minutes%20to%20make%2C%20and%20it