riwal-liquor-policy-scam-russia-ukraine-iran-un-musk-us-elections-124042200089_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findia-news%2Flatest-news-today-live-news-updates-breaking-news-today-top-news-latest-news-pm-modi-lok-sabha-elections-first-phase-general-elections-iran-israel-palestine-arvind-kejriwal-liquor-policy-scam-russia-ukraine-iran-un-musk-us-elections-124042200089_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22PM%20Doubles%20Down%20Amid%20Row%3A%20'Congress%20Will%20Take%20Away%20Your%20Homes%2C%20Jewels'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20massive%20row%20over%20his%20remarks%20at%20Rajasthan's%20Banswara%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20today%20doubled%20down%20on%20his%20property%20redistribution%20charge%20at%20the%20Congress%2C%20alleging%20that%20the%20Opposition%20party%20is%20eyeing%20the%20property%20of%20citizens%20and%20wants%20to%20loot%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20rally%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Aligarh%2C%20he%20said%20members%20of%20the%20INDIA%20Opposition%20bloc%20have%20lost%20all%20hope%20for%20the%20future.%20%26quot%3BThey%20question%20why%20Modi%20talks%20of%20a%20developed%20India%2C%20why%20he%20talks%20of%20making%20India%20the%20world's%20third-largest%20economy.%20These%20people%20don't%20do%20anything%20except%20for%20their%20families%20and%20their%20greed%20for%20power.%20They%20cheat%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20said%20he%20wants%20to%20warn%20the%20country%20against%20Congress's%20manifesto.%20%26quot%3BCongress%20and%20INDI%20alliance%20are%20now%20eyeing%20your%20income%2C%20your%20property%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20Apparently%20referring%20to%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BCongress's%20prince%20has%20said%20that%20if%20they%20form%20the%20government%2C%20they%20will%20do%20investigate%20who%20earns%20how%20much%2C%20owns%20how%20much%20wealth%20and%20how%20many%20houses.%20He%20also%20says%20that%20the%20government%20will%20take%20control%20of%20your%20property%20and%20distribute%20it%20among%20everyone.%20Their%20manifesto%20says%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20manifesto%2C%20which%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20referred%20to%2C%20calls%20for%20a%20nationwide%20socio-economic%20and%20caste%20census%20to%20provide%20the%20data%20foundation%20for%20affirmative%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20Social%20Justice%20section%2C%20the%20manifesto%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BCongress%20has%20been%20the%20most%20vocal%20and%20active%20champion%20of%20the%20progress%20of%20the%20backward%20and%20oppressed%20classes%20and%20castes%20over%20the%20last%20seven%20decades.%20However%2C%20caste%20discrimination%20is%20still%20a%20reality.%20The%20people%20belonging%20to%20the%20SC%2C%20ST%20and%20OBC%20communities%20have%20not%20yet%20been%20able%20to%20catch%20up%20with%20the%20rest%20and%20are%20still%20left%20behind.%20While%20OBC%2C%20SC%20and%20ST%20constitute%20nearly%2070%20per%20cent%20of%20India's%20population%2C%20their%20representation%20in%20high-ranking%20professions%2C%20services%20and%20businesses%20is%20disproportionately%20low.%20No%20progressive%20modern%20society%20should%20tolerate%20such%20inequality%20or%20discrimination%20based%20on%20ancestry%20and%20the%20consequent%20denial%20of%20equal%20opportunity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20manifesto%20says%20that%20if%20elected%2C%20the%20Congress%20will%20conduct%20a%20nationwide%20socio-economic%20and%20caste%20census.%20%26quot%3BCongress%20will%20conduct%20a%20nation-wide%20Socio-Economic%20and%20Caste%20Census%20to%20enumerate%20the%20castes%20and%20sub-castes%20and%20their%20socio-economic%20conditions.%20Based%20on%20the%20data%2C%20we%20will%20strengthen%20the%20agenda%20for%20affirmative%20action.%26quot%3B%20The%20manifesto%20does%20not%20say%20anything%20about%20a%20plan%20to%20redistribute%20private%20property.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20Aligarh%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20repeated%20his%20'mangalsutra'%20remark%2C%20alleging%20that%20the%20Congress%20plans%20to%20change%20the%20law%20and%20take%20away%20women's%20jewellery.%20%26quot%3BThey%20also%20want%20to%20survey%20how%20much%20salaried%20persons%20have%20invested%20in%20fixed%20deposits%2C%20how%20many%20vehicles%20they%20own%2C%20how%20much%20land%20they%20own.%20They%20will%20conduct%20this%20survey%20and%20seize%20your%20property%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20alleged%20that%20if%20someone%20owns%20an%20ancestral%20home%20at%20the%20village%20and%20buys%20a%20flat%20in%20the%20city%2C%20the%20Congress%20will%20take%20away%20one%20of%20the%20houses.%20%26quot%3BCongress%20will%20say%20you%20already%20own%20a%20home%20and%20you%20don't%20need%20another.%20This%20is%20a%20Maoist%20mindset%2C%20a%20Communist%20mindset%2C%20they%20have%20ruined%20many%20nations.%20The%20Congress%20and%20INDI%20alliance%20want%20to%20apply%20this%20in%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister's%20remarks%20in%20Aligarh%20come%20a%20day%20after%20his%20comments%20in%20Rajasthan's%20Banswara%20sparked%20a%20massive%20row.%20Alleging%20that%20the%20Congress%20plans%20to%20conduct%20a%20survey%20and%20redistribute%20private%20property%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20claimed%20that%20when%20the%20Congress%20was%20in%20power%20under%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-manmohan-singh-pms-wealth-to-infiltrators-jab-manmohan-singhs-2006-speech-a-huge-row-5495887%5C%22%3E%20Dr%20Manmohan%20Singh%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it%20said%20Muslims%20have%20the%20first%20right%20on%20the%20country's%20wealth.%20%26quot%3BThis%20means%20that%20they%20will%20gather%20this%20property%20and%20distribute%20it%20among%20people%20who%20have%20more%20children%2C%20among%20infiltrators.%20Will%20your%20hard-earned%20money%20be%20given%20to%20infiltrators%3F%20Do%20you%20accept%20this%3F%26