are%20is%20available%20to%20the%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20including%20specialist%20treatment%20from%20diabetologists%20or%20endocrinologists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal%2C%20who%20was%20arrested%20last%20month%20in%20the%20alleged%20liquor%20policy%20scam%2C%20moved%20the%20court%20last%20week%2C%20claiming%20Tihar%20Jail%20officials%20had%20failed%20to%20provide%20a%20regular%20supply%20of%20insulin%2C%20a%20critical%20drug%20for%20diabetics.%20The%20Chief%20Minister's%20party%20claimed%20a%20%26quot%3Bconspiracy%20to%20kill%26quot%3B%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP%20leader%20has%20said%20he%20has%20been%20prescribed%2050%20units%20of%20insulin%20daily%20-%2028%20in%20the%20morning%20and%2022%20at%20night%20-%20and%20that%20he%20had%20been%20%26quot%3Bdeprived%20of%20the%20life-saving%20drug%20for%2029%20days%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20morning%2C%20he%20said%20his%20blood%20sugar%20level%20was%20between%20250%20and%20320%20mg%2Fdl%3B%20according%20to%20the%20World%20Health%20Organization%20guidelines%20%26quot%3Bexpected%20values%20for%20normal%20fasting%20blood%20glucose%20concentration%20are%20between%2070%20and%20100%20mg%2FdL%20(or%20milligrams%20per%20decilitre)%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%20this%20morning%2C%20sources%20said%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20wrote%20a%20note%20to%20the%20Tihar%20Jail%20Superintendent%20challenging%20the%20release%20of%20a%20statement%20over%20the%20weekend%20that%20said%20doctors%20the%20central%20government-run%20All%20India%20Institute%20of%20Medical%20Sciences%20had%20%26quot%3Bassured%20(the%20Chief%20Minister)%20there%20is%20no%20serious%20concern%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20read%20the%20statement%20of%20Tihar%20administration%20in%20the%20newspaper.%20Both%20statements%20are%20false.%20I%20am%20asking%20for%20insulin%20daily...%20I%20showed%20the%20glucometer%20readings%20(three%20times%20a%20day)%20and%20told%20them%20sugar%20levels%20are%20high...%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAIIMS%20doctors%20never%20said%20there%20is%20nothing%20to%20worry%20about...%20they%20said%20they%20will%20respond%20after%20looking%20at%20the%20(medical)%20data%20and%20(patient)%20history%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20reportedly%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%20the%20arresting%20agency%2C%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%2C%20opposed%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20request%20on%20grounds%20that%20earlier%20meetings%20had%20been%20%26quot%3Bmisused%26quot%3B%3B%20the%20implied%20reference%20is%20to%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20issuing%20instructions%20to%20his%20government%20-%20to%20Health%20Minister%20Saurabh%20Bhardwaj%20and%20PWD%20Minister%20Atishi%20-%20from%20jail%2C%20a%20practice%20the%20opposition%20BJP%20has%20slammed%20as%20unethical.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20also%20claimed%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20had%20deliberately%20eaten%20foods%20high%20in%20sugar%20-%20mangoes%20and%20toffees%20-%20to%20elevate%20his%20blood%20sugar%20level%20and%20establish%20grounds%20for%20medical%20bail.%20The%20ED%20had%20also%20argued%20that%20mangoes%20and%20toffees%20in%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20diet%20violated%20court%20orders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20argument%20last%20week%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20slammed%20the%20ED%20for%20its%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20shocking%20that%20ED%20(believes)%20a%20person%20would%20deliberately%20cause%20such%20alarming%20hikes%20in%20sugar%20level%20and%20risk%20his%20life%20-%20for%20getting%20medical%20bail%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20argued.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20Was%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20Arrested%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArvind%20Kejriwal%20was%20arrested%20by%20the%20ED%20on%20March%2021%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20alleged%20liquor%20policy%20scam%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%20The%20probe%20agency%20believes%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20played%20a%20key%20role%20in%20drafting%20the%20now-scrapped%20policy%20and%20seeking%20bribes%2C%20or