demned%20the%20violence%2C%20but%20some%20criticize%20the%20university%20for%20not%20enforcing%20protest%20guidelines.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fjewish-yale-student-stabbed-in-eye-with-palestine-flag-during-anti-israel-protest-reporting%2Farticleshow%2F109502848.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fjewish-yale-student-stabbed-in-eye-with-palestine-flag-during-anti-israel-protest-reporting%2Famp_articleshow%2F109502848.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fjewish-yale-student-stabbed-in-eye-with-palestine-flag-during-anti-israel-protest-reporting%2Famp_articleshow%2F109502848.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Outrage%20After%20US%20Comedian%20Kicks%20Breastfeeding%20Woman%2C%20Baby%20Out%20Of%20His%20Show%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUS%20Comedian%20Arj%20Barker%20has%20come%20under%20fire%20after%20he%20asked%20a%20mother%20and%20her%20baby%20to%20leave%20his%20stand-up%20set%3Cb%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3Eat%20the%20Melbourne%20International%20Comedy%20Festival.%20According%20to%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2024%2F04%2F22%2Fentertainment%2Fcomedian-arj-barker-kicks-breastfeeding-mother-baby-out-of-his-australia-show-at-athenaeum-theater%2F%5C%22%3ENew%20York%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20incident%20happened%20on%C2%A0April%2020%20when%20Trish%20Faranda%20was%20attending%20the%20comedy%20show%20with%20her%20seven-month-old%20daughter%20Clara%20and%20a%20friend.%20After%20Clara%20made%20a%20few%20gurgling%20sounds%2C%20Mr%20Barker%20stopped%20and%20later%20cracked%20up%20a%20few%20jokes%20about%20the%20situation.%20However%2C%20after%20a%20while%2C%20he%20approached%20the%20mother%20again%20due%20to%20the%20disturbance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''I%20was%20breastfeeding%20when%20he%20came%20and%20stood%20in%20front%20of%20me%20and%20he%20was%20telling%20me%20to%20leave%2C'%20Trish%20said.%20''People%20were%20laughing%20and%20I%20don't%20think%20he%20was%20joking.%20So%20I%20said%20to%20him%2C%20do%20you%20want%20me%20to%20leave%3F%20And%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CYes%20I%20do%2C''%20Ms%20Faranda%20said.%C2%A0After%20she%20exited%20the%20show%2C%20a%20few%20others%20also%20staged%20a%20walkout%20in%20solidarity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHeated%20debate%20on%20social%20media%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20also%20triggered%20a%20heated%20debate%20on%20social%20media.%20While%20some%20said%20that%20the%20woman%20shouldn't%20have%20brought%20a%20baby%20to%20the%20show%2C%20a%20few%20others%20slammed%20the%20comedian%2C%20stressing%20that%20being%20a%20new%20mother%20is%20hard%20and%20he%20should%20have%20shown%20some%20compassion.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAustralian%20politician%20Ellen%20Sandell%20tweeted%3A%20''I%20am%20livid%20at%20hearing%20this.%20It's%20hard%20enough%20for%20new%20mums%20to%20participate%20in%20society%20with%20all%20the%20barriers%20put%20in%20front%20of%20them%20%E2%80%93%20to%20be%20humiliated%20like%20this%2C%20for%20just%20trying%20to%20enjoy%20the%20comedy%20festival%2C%20is%20awful.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20defended%20the%20comedian%20and%20said%2C%20''I'm%20a%20parent%20and%20I%20think%20he%20was%20right%20to%20ask%20her%20to%20leave%20after%20she%20failed%20to%20consider%20the%20other%20paying%20audience%20members.%20Most%20comedy%20shows%20are%20not%20much%20more%20than%20an%20hour.%20Organize%20a%20babysitter%20or%20don't%20go.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EComedian%20defends%20his%20decision%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20US%20comedian%20stood%20by%20the%20''awkward''%20decision%2C%20telling%20people%20that%20''the%20baby%20was%20disrupting%20my%20performance''%20and%20that%20he%20''politely%20told%20her%20the%20baby%20couldn't%20stay.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20baby%20wasn't%20crying%20and%20screaming%2C%20but%20in%20the%20%EF%BB%BFAthenaeum%2C%20sounds%20(does)%20travel%20and%20you%20can%20hear%20the%20drop%20of%20a%20pin.%20The%20woman%20didn't%20even%20know%20if%20I%20was%20serious%2C%20and%20I%20said%20'I%20wasn't%20(joking).%20I%20made%20the%20decision%20for%20the%20audience%20who%20wanted%20to%20see%20the%20show%20and%20also%20I%20shouldn't%20have%20been%20in%20that%20position%2C%20it's%20a%2015%2B%20show%2C''%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20later%20shared%20another%20elaborate%20statement%20on%20Instagram.%C2%A0%26quot%3BIt's%20unfortunate%20about%20any%20embarrassment%20it%20caused%20her%20or%20her%20family%2C%20but%20again%2C%20had%20the%20show%20policy%20been%20adhered%20to%2C%20this%20situation%20would%20not%20have%20occurred%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0He%20also%20offered%20the%20woman%20a%20refund%20for%20the%20ticket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC6DadLmPpcZ%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC6DadLmPpcZ%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC6DadLmPpcZ%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdi