cials%20of%20the%20weather%20office.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Election%20Commissioner%20Rajiv%20Kumar%2C%20along%20with%20Election%20Commissioners%20Gyanesh%20Kumar%20and%20Sukhbir%20Singh%20Sandhu%20chaired%20the%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20meeting%20discussed%20measures%20to%20mitigate%20risk%20due%20to%20heatwaves%20during%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%20Six%20more%20phases%20of%20the%20seven-%20phased%20exercise%20are%20yet%20to%20be%20held%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20view%20of%20forecast%20of%20above%20normal%20temperatures%20%26amp%3B%20heat%20waves%20in%20parts%20of%20the%20country%2C%20Commission%20is%20holding%20a%20meeting%20with%20different%20stakeholders%20this%20morning.%20The%20meeting%20is%20discussing%20measures%20to%20mitigate%20risk%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20of%20the%20poll%20body%20posted%20on%20X%2C%26quot%3B%20adding%20that%20the%20meeting%20was%20attended%20by%20officers%20from%20the%20India%20Meteorological%20Department%20(IMD)%2C%20National%20Disaster%20Management%20Authority%20(NDMA)%20and%20Ministry%20of%20the%20Home%20Affairs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EIn%20view%20of%20forecast%20of%20above%20normal%20temperatures%20%26amp%3B%20heat%20waves%20in%20parts%20of%20the%20country%2C%20Commission%20is%20holding%20a%20meeting%20with%20different%20stakeholders%20this%20morning.%20The%20meeting%20is%20discussing%20measures%20to%20mitigate%20risk.%20Officers%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FiMD%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40IMD%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20NDMA%20and%20MoHFW%20are%20attending%20the%20meeting.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FAwjtrBnNwX%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FAwjtrBnNwX%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Spokesperson%20ECI%20(%40SpokespersonECI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSpokespersonECI%2Fstatus%2F1782294690458443836%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EApril%2022%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20threshold%20for%20a%20heatwave%20is%20met%20when%20the%20maximum%20temperature%20of%20a%20weather%20station%20reaches%20at%20least%2040%20degrees%20Celsius%20in%20the%20plains%2C%2037%20degrees%20in%20the%20coastal%20areas%2C%20and%2030%20degrees%20in%20the%20hilly%20regions%2C%20and%20the%20departure%20from%20normal%20is%20at%20least%204.5%20notches.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20severe%20heatwave%20is%20declared%20if%20the%20departure%20from%20normal%20temperature%20exceeds%206.4%20notches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIMD%20is%20in%20continuous%20touch%20with%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India.%20Along%20with%20seasonal%20forecasts%2C%20we%20are%20doing%20monthly%2C%20week-wise%20and%20everyday%20forecasts%20and%20giving%20them%20forecasts%20about%20heat%20waves%2C%20and%20humidity%20levels.%20We%20are%20providing%20the%20ECI%2C%20inputs%20and%20forecasts%20about%20the%20places%20where%20elections%20are%20going%20to%20be%20held%20in%20different%20phases%2C%26quot%3B%20Director%20General%20of%20Meteorology%20of%20the%20India%20Meteorological%20Department%20(IMD)%20Mrutyunjay%20Mohapatra%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20April%2011%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20had%20chaired%20a%20meeting%20to%20review%20preparedness%20for%20the%20ensuing%20heat%20wave%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20weather%20office%20IMD%20had%20issued%20an%20updated%20Seasonal%20Outlook%20for%20the%20hot%20weather%20season%20(April%20to%20June)%202024%2C%20in%20which%20it%20said%2C%20above%20Normal%20maximum%20temperatures%20are%20likely%20over%20most%20parts%20of%20the%20country%2C%20especially%20with%20high%20probability%20over%20central%20India%20and%20western%20peninsular%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20phase%20will%20be%20held%20on%20April%2026%20and%20the%20remaining%20phases%20will%20be%20May%207%2C%20May%2013%2C%20May%2020%2C%20May%2025%20and%20June%201%20accordi