2%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fhome%2Fscience%2Ffrom-apollo-to-artemis-why-its-so-difficult-to-send-humans-to-moon%2Famp_articleshow%2F109500019.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'How%20Did%20He%20Know%3F'%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20Targets%20Ex%20Aide%20After%20Court%20Setback%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EHours%20after%20the%20West%20Bengal%20government%20suffered%20a%20big%20setback%20in%20Calcutta%20High%20Court%20in%20connection%20with%20alleged%20irregularities%20in%20teachers'%20recruitment%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20alleged%20that%20BJP%20leaders%20are%20%26quot%3Binfluencing%20judiciary%20and%20judgments%26quot%3B.%20The%20big%20charge%20came%20after%20the%20court%C2%A0declared%20as%20null%20and%20void%20the%202016%20recruitment%20of%20about%2025%2C000%20school%20staff%20by%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Opposition%20BJP%20has%20welcomed%20the%20high%20court's%20order.%20%26quot%3BThe%20deserving%20candidates%20are%20smiling%2C%20now%20it's%20time%20for%20nephew%20and%20aunt%20to%20go%2C%26quot%3B%20Bengal%20BJP%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20taking%20a%20swipe%20at%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20and%20nephew%20and%20senior%20Trinamool%20Congress%20leader%20Abhishek%20Banerjee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Banerjee%20asked%20the%20sacked%20school%20staff%20not%20to%20worry.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20with%20you%2C%20we%20will%20fight.%2026%2C000%20teachers%20means%201.5%20lakh%20families.%20They%20have%20worked%20for%20eight%20years.%20How%20will%20they%20return%20salaries%20in%20four%20weeks%3F%26quot%3B%20The%20West%20Bengal%20school%20service%20commission%20has%20already%20said%20they%20will%20challenge%20the%20high%20court%20ruling%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20scathing%20attack%20on%20BJP's%20Suvendu%20Adhikari%2C%20once%20her%20trusted%20lieutenant%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BHe%20predicted%20a%C2%A0%20bomb.%20What%20is%20the%20bomb%3F%20Snatching%20the%20jobs%20of%2026%2C000%20people%20and%20pushing%20them%20towards%20death.%20How%20did%20they%20know%20what%20the%20court%20will%20rule%20if%20they%20did%20not%20write%20the%20judgment%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Banerjee%20was%20referring%20to%20Mr%20Adhikari's%20prediction%20last%20week%20of%20a%20political%20%26quot%3Bexplosion%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BWait%20for%20Monday.%20A%20huge%20explosion%20will%20shatter%20Pisi-Bhaipo's%20party.%20They%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20recover%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20Bengal%20Assemblly%20told%20party%20workers%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20reporters'%20queries%20on%20his%20remark%2C%20Mr%20Adhikari%20had%20clarified%20that%20he%20was%20referring%20to%20a%20political%20upheaval%20and%20insisted%20that%20the%20Trinamool%20was%20in%20a%20precarious%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20division%20bench%20of%20Justice%20Debangsu%20Basak%20and%20Md%20Shabbar%20Rashidi%20today%20trashed%20appointments%20made%20after%20State%20Level%20Selection%20Test-2016%20to%20fill%20up%20teachers'%20posts%20in%20Bengal's%20government-sponsored%20and%20aided%20schools.%20The%20court%20asked%20the%20CBI%20to%20investigate%20the%20appointment%20process%20and%20submit%20a%20report%20in%20three%20months.%20The%20West%20Bengal%20School%20Service%20Commission%2C%20which%20recruits%20staff%20for%20state-run%20schools%2C%20has%20been%20asked%20to%20initiate%20a%20fresh%20appointment%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20total%20of%2023%20lakh%20candidates%20had%20appeared%20for%20the%202016%20recruitment%20exam%20for%2024%2C640%20posts.%20A%20total%20of%2025%2C753%20appointment%20letters%20were%20issued%20against%20the%20vacancies.%20These%20appointments%20have%20now%20been%20declared%20null%20and%20void%20and%20the%20teachers%20have%20been%20asked%20to%20return%20the%20salary%20they%20have%20received%20so%20far%20with%20interest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20the%20high%20court%20verdict%2C%20Trinamool's%20Kunal%20Ghosh%20earlier%20said%20that%20while%20wrongdoers%20should%20be%20punished%2C%20the%20deserving%20candidates%20should%20not%20be%20penalised.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20government%20has%20worked%20sincerely%20for%20creating%20jobs.%20An%20attempt%20to%20address%20some%20irregularities%20must%20not%20push%20deserving%20candidates%20into%20uncertainty.%20They%20need%20jobs%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHundreds%20of%20school%20job%20aspirants%2C%20who%20had%20protested%20against%20alleged%20irregularities%20in%20teachers'%20recruitment%2C%20had%20gathered%20outside%20the%20court.%20Many%20of%20them%20broke%20into%20tears.%20%26quot%3BWe%20had%20been%20waiting%20for%20this%20day.%20After%20years%20of%20struggle%20on%20the%20streets%2C%20justice%20has%20finally%20been%20delivered%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20of%20them%20told%20news%20agency%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdvocate%20Bikram%20Banerjee%2C%20counsel%20for%20one%20of%20the%20petitioners%2C%20told%20news%20agency%20ANI%2C%20%26quot%3BParticularly%2C%20the%20tender%20process%20was%20given%20to%20a%20blacklisted%20company%2C%20namely%20NYSA%2C%20and%20that%20process%20is%20illegal.%20The%20number%20of%20illegal%20appointees%20can%20not%20be%20detected%2C%20in%20view%20of%20which%20the%20entire%20selection%20process%20has%20been%20cancelled.%20The%20beneficiaries%20of%20this%20illegal%20process%20must%20refund%20their%20salaries.%20The%20district%20collectors%20of%20all%20districts%20in%20West%20Bengal%20have%20been%20directed%20to%20start%20the%20recovery%20process%20within%20four%20weeks.%20A%20fresh%20selection%20process%20must%20be%20started.%20A%20fresh%20tender%20must%20be%20publicly%20advertised.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDuring%20the%20process%2C%20a%20super-numerical%20post%20was%20created%20by%20the%20state%20of%20West%20Bengal.%20Given%20the%20illegal%20appointees%2C%20the%20state%20of%20Bengal%20tried%20to%20accommodate%20them%2C%20but%20this%20was%20purely%20illegal.%20The%20Division%20Bench%20has%20directed%20to%20investigate%20and%20find%20out%20who%20created%20the%20super-numerical%20post.%20If%20necessary%2C%20the%20influential%20person%20will%20be%20taken%20into%20custody%20by%20CBI%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHearing%20in%20the%20matter%20ended%20on%20March%2020%20and%20the%20court%20had%20reserved%20its%20judgment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20writ%20petitions%20challenging%20the%20appointments%20had%20been%20filed%20by%20candidates%20who%20appeared%20for%20the%20recruitment%20exam%2C%20but%20did%20not%20get%20jobs.%20A%20single%20bench%20of%20Justice%20Abhijit%20Gangopadhyay%2C%20who%20has%20now%20quit%20judiciary%20and%20joined%20the%20BJP%2C%20had%20ordered%20a%20CBI%20investigation%20into%20the%20alleged%20irregularities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20matter%20had%20also%20reached%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20which%20had%20asked%20the%20high%20court%20to%20constitute%20a%20division%20bench%20to%20hear%20petitions%20related%20to%20the%20recruitment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20is%20investigating%20the%20matter.%20It%20has%20arrested%20former%20education%20minister%20and%20Trinamool%20heavyweight%20Partha%20Chatterjee%2C%20and%20several%20officials%20of%20the%20school%20service%20commission.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713779880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F5v7a1r8o_mamata-suvendu-split_625x300_22_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcalcutta-high-court-mamata-banerjee-bjps-aunt-nephew-dig-at-mamata-banerjee-as-court-sacks-25-000-teachers-5496554%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20BJP%20has%20welcomed%20the%20Calcutta%20High%20Court's%20order%20declaring%20as%20null%20and%20void%20the%202016%20recruitment%20of%20about%2025%2C000%20teachers%20by%20the%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20government.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canoni