Record-Breaking%20Rally%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EGold's%20rise%20to%20all-time%20highs%20above%20%242%2C400%20an%20ounce%20this%20year%20has%20captivated%20global%20markets.%20China%2C%20the%20world's%20biggest%20producer%20and%20consumer%20of%20the%20precious%20metal%2C%20is%20front%20and%20center%20of%20the%20extraordinary%20ascent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWorsening%20geopolitical%20tensions%2C%20including%20war%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20and%20Ukraine%2C%20and%20the%20prospect%20of%20lower%20US%20interest%20rates%20all%20burnish%20gold's%20billing%20as%20an%20investment.%20But%20juicing%20the%20rally%20is%20unrelenting%20Chinese%20demand%2C%20as%20retail%20shoppers%2C%20fund%20investors%2C%20futures%20traders%20and%20even%20the%20central%20bank%20look%20to%20bullion%20as%20a%20store%20of%20value%20in%20uncertain%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBiggest%20Buyer%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%20and%20India%20have%20typically%20vied%20over%20the%20title%20of%20world's%20biggest%20buyer.%20But%20that%20shifted%20last%20year%20as%20Chinese%20consumption%20of%20jewelry%2C%20bars%20and%20coins%20swelled%20to%20record%20levels.%20China's%20gold%20jewelry%20demand%20rose%2010%25%20while%20India's%20fell%206%25.%20Chinese%20bar%20and%20coin%20investments%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20surged%2028%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20there's%20still%20room%20for%20demand%20to%20grow%2C%20said%20Philip%20Klapwijk%2C%20managing%20director%20of%20Hong%20Kong-based%20consultant%20Precious%20Metals%20Insights%20Ltd.%20Amid%20limited%20investment%20options%20in%20China%2C%20the%20protracted%20crisis%20in%20its%20property%20sector%2C%20volatile%20stock%20markets%20and%20a%20weakening%20yuan%20are%20all%20driving%20money%20to%20assets%20that%20are%20perceived%20to%20be%20safer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20weight%20of%20money%20available%20under%20these%20circumstances%20for%20an%20asset%20like%20gold%20-%20and%20actually%20for%20new%20buyers%20to%20come%20in%20-%20is%20pretty%20considerable%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere%20isn't%20much%20alternative%20in%20China.%20With%20exchange%20controls%20and%20capital%20controls%2C%20you%20can't%20just%20look%20at%20other%20markets%20to%20put%20your%20money%20into.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EImports%20Jump%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20China%20mines%20more%20gold%20than%20any%20other%20country%2C%20it%20still%20needs%20to%20import%20a%20lot%20and%20the%20quantities%20are%20getting%20larger.%20In%20the%20last%20two%20years%2C%20overseas%20purchases%20totaled%20over%202%2C800%20tons%20-%20more%20than%20all%20of%20the%20metal%20that%20backs%20exchange-traded%20funds%20around%20the%20world%2C%20or%20about%20a%20third%20of%20the%20stockpiles%20held%20by%20the%20US%20Federal%20Reserve.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20so%2C%20the%20pace%20of%20shipments%20has%20accelerated%20lately.%20Imports%20surged%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20China's%20Lunar%20New%20Year%2C%20a%20peak%20season%20for%20gifts%2C%20and%20over%20the%20first%20three%20months%20of%20the%20year%20are%2034%25%20higher%20than%20they%20were%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECentral%20Bank%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20People's%20Bank%20of%20China%20has%20been%20on%20a%20buying%20spree%20for%2017%20straight%20months%2C%20its%20longest-ever%20run%20of%20purchases%2C%20as%20it%20looks%20to%20diversify%20its%20reserves%20away%20from%20the%20dollar%20and%20hedge%20against%20currency%20depreciation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20the%20keenest%20buyer%20among%20a%20number%20central%20banks%20that%20are%20favoring%20gold.%20The%20official%20sector%20snapped%20up%20near-record%20levels%20of%20the%20precious%20metal%20last%20year%20and%20is%20expected%20to%20keep%20purchases%20elevated%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EShanghai%20Premium%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20indicative%20of%20gold's%20allure%20that%20Chinese%20demand%20remains%20so%20buoyant%2C%20despite%20record%20prices%20and%20a%20weaker%20yuan%20that%20robs%20buyers%20of%20purchasing%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20major%20importer%2C%20gold%20buyers%20in%20China%20often%20have%20to%20pay%20a%20premium%20over%20international%20prices.%20That%20jumped%20to%20%2489%20an%20ounce%20at%20the%20start%20of%20the%20month.%20The%20average%20over%20the%20past%20year%20is%20%2435%20versus%20a%20historical%20average%20of%20just%20%247.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20sure%2C%20sky-high%20prices%20are%20likely%20to%20temper%20some%20enthusiasm%20for%20bullion%2C%20but%20the%20market's%20proving%20to%20be%20unusually%20resilient.%20Chinese%20consumers%20have%20typically%20snapped%20up%20gold%20when%20prices%20drop%2C%20which%20has%20helped%20establish%20a%20floor%20for%20the%20market%20during%20times%20of%20weakness.%20Not%20so%20this%20time%2C%20as%20China's%20appetite%20is%20helping%20to%20prop%20up%20prices%20at%20much%20higher%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20suggests%20the%20rally%20is%20sustainable%20and%20gold%20buyers%20everywhere%20should%20be%20comforted%20by%20China's%20booming%20demand%2C%20said%20Nikos%20Kavalis%2C%20managing%20director%20at%20consultancy%20Metals%20Focus%20Ltd.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina's%20authorities%2C%20which%20can%20be%20quite%20hostile%20to%20market%20speculation%2C%20are%20less%20sanguine.%20State%20media%20have%20warned%20investors%20to%20be%20cautious%20in%20chasing%20the%20rally%2C%20while%20both%20the%20Shanghai%20Gold%20Exchange%20and%20Shanghai%20Futures%20Exchange%20have%20raised%20margin%20requirements%20on%20some%20contracts%20to%20snuff%20out%20excessive%20risk-taking.%20SHFE's%20move%20followed%20a%20surge%20in%20daily%20trading%20volumes%20to%20a%20five-year%20high.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EETF%20Flows%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20less%20frenetic%20way%20to%20invest%20in%20gold%20is%20via%20exchange-traded%20funds.%20Money%20has%20flowed%20into%20gold%20ETFs%20in%20mainland%20China%20during%20almost%20every%20month%20since%20June%2C%20according%20to%20Bloomberg%20Intelligence.%20That%20compares%20with%20chunky%20outflows%20in%20gold%20funds%20in%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20influx%20of%20money%20has%20totaled%20%241.3%20billion%20so%20far%20this%20year%2C%20compared%20with%20%244%20billion%20in%20outflows%20from%20funds%20overseas.%20Restrictions%20on%20investing%20in%20China%20are%20again%20a%20factor%20here%2C%20given%20the%20fewer%20options%20for%20Chinese%20beyond%20domestic%20property%20and%20stocks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChinese%20demand%20could%20continue%20to%20rise%20as%20investors%20look%20to%20diversify%20their%20holdings%20with%20commodities%2C%20BI%20analyst%20Rebecca%20Sin%20said%20in%20a%20note.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOn%20the%20Wire%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChile%20imposed%20temporary%20anti-dumping%20tariffs%20on%20Chinese%20steel%20products%20used%20in%20the%20country's%20mining%20industry%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20support%20faltering%20local%20producers.%20The%20move%20pushed%20Cap%20SA%20to%20reverse%20a%20decision%20to%20wind%20down%20its%20steel%20mills.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina's%20most-promising%20industries%20are%20facing%20a%20growing%20threat%20of%20trade%20restrictions%20from%20Western%20governments%2C%20blurring%20the%20outlook%20for%20stocks%20that%20have%20the%20potential%20to%20fuel%20the%20nation's%20market%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Beijing%20already%20becoming%20a%20top%20target%20in%20the%20US%20election%20campaign%2C%20President%20Xi%20Jinping's%20government%20is%20resisting%20any%20move%20that%20could%20backfire%20on%20the%20world's%20second-largest%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20introduce%20a%20raft%20of%20tariffs%20and%20restrictions%20to%20protect%20domestic%20industries%2C%20you'd%20better%20make%20sure%20there%20are%20some%20around%20to%20protect.%20That's%20a%20major%20problem%20with%20the%20US%20decision%20to%20treat%20China's%20clean%20technology%20leadership%20as%20grounds%20for%20a%20trade%20fight.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713776880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fnu53mldg_gold_625x300_22_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchina-is-front-and-center-of-golds-record-breaking-rally-5496730%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22China%2C%20the%20world's%20biggest%20producer%20and%20consumer%20of%20the%20precious%20metal%2C%20is%20front%20and%20center%20of%20the%20extraordinary%20ascent.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchina-is-front-and-center-of-golds-record-breaking-rally-5496730%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Iran's%20president%20holds%20talks%20with%20Pakistani%20premier%20after%20arrival%20in%20Islamabad%20for%20a%203-day%20visit%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713776811000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-109498289%2Cimgsize-823390.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Firans-president-holds-talks-with-pakistani-premier-after-arrival-in-islamabad-for-a-3-day-visit%2Farticleshow%2F109498164.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F109498164.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Firans-president-holds-talks-with-pakistani-premier-after-arrival-in-islamabad-for-a-3-day-visit%2Farticleshow%2F109498164.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Firans-president-holds-talks-with-pakistani-premier-after-arrival-in-islamabad-for-a-3-day-visit%2Famp_articleshow%2F109