%2C%20he%20has%20been%20living%20in%20Ahmedabad%20since%202004%20when%20he%20joined%20NID.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20enjoys%20classical%2C%20Sufi%2C%20and%20Rajasthani%20folk%20music.%20While%20he%20used%20to%20play%20sports%20in%20school%2C%20today%20he%20occasionally%20finds%20time%20for%20video%20games.%20He%20likes%20watching%20movies%2C%20mostly%20Bollywood%20dramas%20and%20comedies.%20He%20prefers%20low-budget%20films%2C%20which%20do%20not%20feature%20big%20stars%20%E2%80%94%20a%20recent%20favourite%20is%20%E2%80%9812%3Csup%3Eth%3C%2Fsup%3E%20Fail%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERegarding%20work-life%20balance%2C%20Satya%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CRunning%20my%20own%20business%20affords%20me%20the%20flexibility%20to%20work%20on%20my%20own%20terms.%20Also%2C%20I%20find%20immense%20joy%20in%20what%20I%20do%2C%20which%20blurs%20the%20lines%20between%20work%20and%20leisure%20for%20me.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713536984000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FAkhand-Multiscript_11zon-1713535979-2048x2048.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D347869%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Recognising%20the%20linguistic%20diversity%20of%20India%2C%20with%20its%20multitude%20of%20languages%20and%20over%2011%20official%20writing%20systems%2C%20Satya%20Rajpurohit%20started%20the%20Indian%20Type%20Foundry%20(ITF)%20in%20Ahmedabad%20to%20create%20high-quality%20Indian%20fonts.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Aruna%20Raghuram%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F347869%2Fsatya-rajpurohit-nid-grad-ahmedabad-indian-type-foundry-traditional-fonts-apple-google-samsung%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Elections%202024%3A%20What%20Makes%20Voter%20Ink%20So%20Difficult%20to%20Remove%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20beginning%20of%