3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC57XwBsBAPe%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20The%20Better%20India%20(%40thebetterindia)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20ink%20touches%20the%20surface%20of%20our%20skin%2C%20the%20silver%20nitrate%20reacts%20with%20the%20natural%20salts%20in%20our%20body%20and%20turns%20into%20silver%20chloride.%20This%20reaction%20happens%20in%20just%2040%20seconds!%20Once%20the%20silver%20chloride%20is%20formed%2C%20it%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20washed%20away%20with%20water%20and%20can%20remain%20on%20the%20skin%20for%202%20to%2030%20days.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20amount%20of%20silver%20nitrate%20in%20the%20ink%20is%20between%207%20to%2025%20percent%20but%20the%20exact%20amount%20is%20never%20revealed%20by%20the%20government.%20Also%20known%20as%20the%20indelible%20ink%2C%20it%20was%20first%20made%20by%20the%20National%20Physical%20Laboratory%20in%20Delhi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sole%20manufacturer%20of%20the%20ink%20has%20been%20Mysore%20Paints%20and%20Varnish%20Limited.%20According%20to%20a%20report%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Times%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F137858%2Felection-commission-beggars-homeless-undertrials-poll-process%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20Election%20Commission%20%3C%2Fa%3Ehas%20ordered%20more%20than%2026%20lakh%20vials%20for%20the%20election%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20states%20that%20a%20single%20vile%20of%2010%20mg%20can%20cover%20as%20many%20as%20700%20voters.%20A%20report%20by%20%3Cem%3EFirst%20Post%20%3C%2Fem%3Estates%20that%20the%20cost%20of%20buying%20this%20ink%20is%20Rs%2055%20crore.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713525467000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D347774%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Elections%202024%3A%20The%20voter%20ink%20or%20the%20indelible%20ink%20can%20stay%20on%20a%20voter's%20finger%20anywhere%20between%202%20to%2030%20days.%20Here's%20what%20it%20is%20made%20of!%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F347774%2Flok-sabha-election-2024-voting-ink-indelible-mark-facts-to-know-before-voting%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98There%E2%80%99s%20No%20Age%20Limit%20For%20Learning%E2%80%99%3A%20Started%20at%2063%2C%20Woman%20Earns%20Lakhs%20Growing%20Saffron%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20May%202023%2C%20Shubha%20Bhatnagar%20initiated%20a%20rather%20interesting%20dinner%20table%20conversation.%20She%20shared%20her%20dream%20of%20cultivating%20saffron%20indoors%20and%20providing%20employment%20to%20rural%20women%20in%20the%20nearby%20villages.%20A%20homemaker%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F335137%2Fsenior-citizens-travel-life-after-retirement-trekking-riding-travelling-biking-road-trips%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E63-year-old%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewas%20%E2%80%9Cfree%20of%20responsibilities%E2%80%9D%20and%20wished%20to%20embark%20upon%20a%20journey%20of%20self-reliance%20by%20becoming%20an%20agriprenuer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20dinner%20table%20were%20two%20engineers%3A%20her%20son%20and%20daughter-in-law%2C%20and%20her%20husband%2C%20who%20runs%20a%20cold%20storage%20business.%20They%20were%20intrigued%20by%20her%20idea%20and%20immediately%20started%20looking%20at%20how%20to%20make%20her%20vision%20a%20reality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConversations%20in%20the%20following%20weeks%20and%20months%20that%20followed%20were%20no%20longer%20about%20the%20everyday%20mundanities%2C%20but%20rather%20about%20how%20saffron%20could%20be%20cultivated%20indoors%20and%20how%20they%20could%20achieve%20the%20necessary%20climatic%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaffron%2C%20a%20highly%20valued%20spice%2C%20is%20exclusively%20grown%20in%20Kashmir%2C%20benefiting%20from%20its%20unique%20soil%20and%20weather%20conditions.%20Through%20trial%20and%20error%2C%20they%20replicated%20the%20climatic%20conditions%20of%20Kashmir%20in%20a%20cold%20storage%20room%20in%20Mainpuri%20using%20IoT%20(Internet%20Of%20Things).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThus%2C%20by%20integrating%20technology%2C%20they%20planted%20the%20authentically%20sourced%20seeds%20in%20the%20cold%20storage%20chamber%20in%20August%202023%2C%20yielding%20their%20first%20harvest%20approximately%20three%20months%20later.%20Named%20%E2%80%98Shubhavni%20SmartFarms%2C%E2%80%99%20they%20commenced%20selling%20their%20first%20produce%20of%20two%20kilograms%20of%20saffron%20earlier%20this%20year.%20They%20have%20sold%20over%20Rs%208%20lakh%20worth%20of%20saffron%20and%20employed%2025%20women%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%E2%80%99s%20how%20Shubha%20achieved%20this%20remarkable%20feat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20business%20trip%20to%20Kashmir%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20completing%20her%20MA%20(Master%20of%20Arts)%20in%20Hindi%20from%20Shikohabad%2C%20Shubha%20got%20married%20and%20moved%20to%20Mainpuri.%20She%20spent%20the%20next%2040%20years%20of%20her%20life%20taking%20care%20of%20her%20two%20children%3A%20a%20son%20and%20daughter%2C%20and%20later%20her%20grandchildren.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fsaffron-shubha-min-1713440185.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Shubha%20started%20growing%20saffron%20indoors%20last%20year%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fsaffron-shubha-min-1713440185.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fsaffron-shubha-min-1713440185-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fsaffron-shubha-min-1713440185-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fsaffron-shubha-min-1713440185-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fsaffron-shubha-min-1713440185-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-347649%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EShubha%20started%20growing%20saffron%20indoors%20last%20year%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20only%20in%20the%20past%20few%20years%20that%20she%20started%20looking%20for%20avenues%20to%20start%20a%20business.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20to%20put%20my%20time%20and%20life%20to%20good%20use.%20Luckily%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20healthy%20and%20ready%20to%20do%20some%20hard%20work.%20At%20this%20stage%20of%20life%2C%20I%20want%20to%20find%20some%20purpose%20and%20meaning%20to%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Shubha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20agriculture%20is%20a%20major%20occupation%20in%20Mainpuri%2C%20she%20started%20looking%20at%20possible%20options%20of%20crops%20that%20could%20be%20grown%20indoors%2C%20thanks%20to%20her%20husband%E2%80%99s%20business%20because%20cold%20storage%20is%20a%20requirement%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F346387%2Forganic-farmer-namakkal-tamil-nadu-hydroponics-maize-fodder-drip-irrigation-p-saravanan%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eindoor%20farming.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20would%20often%20meet%20farmers%20and%20women%20who%20worked%20as%20helpers%20in%20fields.%20They%20had%20a%20tough%20time%20providing%20for%20their%20families%20and%20educating%20their%20women.%20I%20wanted%20to%20employ%20these%20women%20through%20whatever%20venture%20I%20began%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shubha%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20finally%20shortlisted%20mushrooms%20and%20saffron%20after%20months%20of%20research%20and%20feasibility%20studies%2C%20and%20decided%20to%20go%20ahead%20with%20saffron.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKnown%20as%20%3Cem%3Ekesar%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20Hindi%2C%20saffron%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20expensive%20spices%20globally.%20Iran%20holds%20the%20title%20of%20the%20largest%20producer%20of%20saffron%2C%20with%20India%20following%20suit.%20Within%20India%2C%20this%20spice%20finds%20cultivation%20exclusively%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20owing%20to%20its%20favourable%20climate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShubha%E2%80%99s%20son%20Ankit%20started%20researching%20ways%20to%20grow%20the%20spice%20indoors%20using%20aeroponics.%20He%20also%20looked%20into%20the%20technology%20and%20sensors%20needed%20to%20monitor%20the%20crop.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202560px)%20100vw%2C%202560px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fsaffron-1713440126-scaled.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222560%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20saffron%20is%20grown%20in%20a%20cold%20room%20in%20Mainpuri%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fsaffron-1713440126-scaled.jpeg%202560w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fsaffron-1713440126-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fsaffron-1713440126-500x375.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fsaffron-1713440126-768x576.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fsaffron-1713440126-1536x1152.jpeg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fsaffron-1713440126-2048x1536.jpeg%202048w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fsaffron-1713440126-150x113.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-347645%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20saffron%20is%20grown%20in%20a%20cold%20room%20in%20Mainpuri%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Shubha%20faced%20a%20dilemma%20regarding%20procuring%20seeds%20or%20saffron%20bulbs.%20She%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20content%20with%20simply%20ordering%20them%20from%20Kashmir%20without%20assessing%20the%20quality%20and%20gaining%20insights%20from%20local%20farmers.%20To%20address%20this%2C%20the%20family%20embarked%20on%20a%20trip%20to%20Kashmir%20for%20a%20week%2C%20engaging%20with%20farmers%2C%20immersing%20themselves%20in%20the%20cultivation%20process%2C%20and%20learning%20the%20dos%20and%20don%E2%80%99ts%20directly%20from%20the%20locals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20met%20about%2025%20to%2030%20farmers%20in%20Kashmir%20and%20spent%20many%20days%20with%20them.%20We%20wanted%20to%20learn%20about%20the%20kind%20of%20soil%20they%20use%2C%20the%20process%20of%20cultivating%20saffron%2C%20how%20long%20it%20takes%2C%20and%20which%20temperatures%20saffron%20thrives%20in.%20We%20also%20bought%20the%20bulbs%20from%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ankit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20coming%20back%2C%20Shubha%20set%20up%20a%20cold%20storage%20room%20of%20560%20square%20feet%20and%20started%20with%202%2C000%20kg%20of%20saffron%20bulbs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20do%20you%20grow%20saffron%20indoors%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20getting%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F345755%2Fhow-to-grow-saffron-at-home-indoors-ramesh-gera-noida-akarshak-institute-online-course%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaffron%20bulbs%20from%20Kashmir%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20look%20like%20garlic%20pods%2C%20the%20first%20step%20was%20to%20dry%20them%20in%20a%20room%20and%20later%20aerate%20them%20for%20three%20days.%20They%20had%20to%20be%20checked%2C%20cleaned%20and%20turned%20every%20few%20hours%20by%20hand%2C%20which%20is%20traditionally%20done%20by%20women%20in%20Kashmir.%20Each%20seed%20was%20checked%20for%20moisture%20and%20rot%2C%20and%20any%20extra%20skin%20was%20removed%20through%20a%20process%20called%20silvering.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fsaffron-shubha-2-1713440142.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Maintaining%20the%20right%20temperature%20is%20crucial%20in%20saffron%20cultivation%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fsaffron-shubha-2-1713440142.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fsaffron-shubha-2-1713440142-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fsaffron-shubha-2-1713440142-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fsaffron-shubha-2-1713440142-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fsaffron-shubha-2-1713440142-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-347648%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EMaintaining%20the%20right%20temperature%20is%20crucial%20in%20saffron%20cultivation%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20seeds%20were%20aerated%2C%20they%20were%20placed%20in%20a%20cold%20room%20in%20vertical%20trays%20on%20racks.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20should%20be%20no%20water%2C%20moisture%20or%20humidity%2C%E2%80%9D%20informs%20Ankit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bulbs%20started%20growing%20and%20buds%20emerged%20after%20a%20few%20days.%20Then%2C%20the%20challenge%20was%20to%20know%20when%20to%20provide%20light%20to%20the%20buds%20and%20at%20what%20temperature.%20While%20the%20beautiful%20valleys%20of%20Kashmir%20provide%20the%20perfect%20ambience%20which%20the%20buds%20enjoy%2C%20replicating%20them%201%2C200%20km%20away%20was%20a%20massive%20task.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20Kashmir%2C%20the%20bud%20receives%20light%20only%20when%20it%20comes%20out%20of%20the%20soil.%20Learning%20at%20what%20stage%20that%20happens%20and%20providing%20the%20right%20temperature%20was%20the%20biggest%20challenge.%20When%20we%20started%2C%20we%20placed%20bulbs%20in%2018%20racks%20in%20six%20rows%20and%20provided%20different%20temperatures%20and%20light%20to%20each%20rack%20to%20judge%20which%20one%20worked%20the%20best%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Ankit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20achieve%20this%2C%20Shubha%20and%20Ankit%20went%20through%2010%20years%20of%20saffron%20production%20data%20in%20Kashmir.%20They%20found%20that%20the%20best%20harvest%20was%20achieved%20in%202015-16%20and%20replicated%20the%20temperatures%20of%20that%20year.%20They%20developed%20a%20programme%20using%20IoT%20devices%20and%20sensors%20to%20maintain%20the%20right%20conditions%20and%20a%20controlled%20environment%20through%20aeroponics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20about%2060%20days%2C%20the%20beautiful%20purple%20flower%20emerged%20and%20was%20ready%20for%20harvest!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fsaffron-1713440138.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20saffron%20from%20Shubhavni%20farms%20is%20sold%20online%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-m