%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EGirls%20at%20Kranti%20get%20an%20opportunity%20to%20achieve%20their%20potential%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20broke%20my%20heart%20to%20see%20girls%20with%20so%20much%20potential%20wasting%20their%20lives%20due%20to%20lack%20of%20access%20to%20resources%20and%20opportunities.%20They%20were%20usually%20just%20married%20off.%20With%20another%20person%20I%20met%20at%20the%20NGO%2C%20Bani%2C%20we%20started%20Kranti%20in%202011%2C%20to%20enable%20these%20girls%20to%20achieve%20their%20full%20potential%2C%E2%80%9D%20Robin%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20word%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Ekranti%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20means%20revolution%20and%20the%20girls%20at%20the%20NGO%20are%20called%20%3Cem%3EKrantikaris%3C%2Fem%3E%20meaning%20revolutionaries.%20Robin%20realised%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F315650%2Fforced-into-sex-work-karnataka-sex-worker-helps-hundreds-get-rights-fight-violence%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egirls%20from%20Kamathipura%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20other%20red-light%20areas%20have%20immense%20potential%20to%20be%20agents%20of%20change%2C%20not%20%E2%80%98despite%E2%80%99%20their%20background%2C%20but%20rather%20because%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20believe%20that%20by%20providing%20access%20to%20the%20same%20training%2C%20opportunities%2C%20and%20resources%20as%20people%20from%20privileged%20backgrounds%2C%20they%20will%20become%20revolutionary%20leaders%20%E2%80%94%20more%20innovative%2C%20compassionate%2C%20and%20resilient%20due%20to%20their%20life%20experiences.%20We%20want%20to%20harness%20their%20power%20as%20agents%20of%20social%20change%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Robin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKranti%20provides%20shelter%2C%20education%2C%20support%20and%20opportunities%20for%20girls%20between%20the%20ages%20of%2012%20and%2021.%20Kranti%20has%20its%20