2%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EKranti%20runs%20its%20own%20school%20for%20the%20girls%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20job%20is%20to%20prepare%20every%20girl%20for%20what%20she%20wants%20to%20do%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%20Every%20girl%20who%20comes%20to%20Kranti%20first%20has%20to%20take%20therapy%2C%20just%20like%20Sandhya%20did%20when%20she%20joined%20in%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20news%20item%20that%20caught%20Sandhya%E2%80%99s%20eye%20was%20of%20Shweta%20Katti%2C%20a%20Krantikari%2C%20who%20made%20waves%20across%20the%20world%20when%20she%20became%20the%20first%20girl%20from%20an%20Indian%20red-light%20district%20to%20secure%20an%20international%20scholarship%20and%20study%20abroad%20at%20Bard%20College%20in%20New%20York.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESandhya%20immediately%20reached%20out%20to%20Shweta%2C%20who%20asked%20her%20to%20message%20Robin%2C%20who%20responded%20with%20a%20one-line%20message%3A%20%E2%80%9CCatch%20the%20first%20train%20and%20come%20to%20Kranti%E2%80%9D.%20It%20took%20Sandhya%20a%20good%20year%20and%20a%20half%20to%20convince%20her%20parents%20before%20she%20knocked%20on%20Kranti%E2%80%99s%20door%20in%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEverybody%20in%20Kranti%20has%20to%20do%20therapy.%20Therapy%20is%20the%20light%20in%20my%20life%3B%20it%20changed%20my%20entire%20worldview%20and%20enabled%20me%20to%20love%20myself%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sandhya%2C%20%E2%80%9CTherapy%20helps%20us%20to%20deal%20with%20our%20trauma%20so%20that%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20carry%20it%20in%20our%20higher%20education.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMental%20health%20is%20the%20biggest%20focus%20initially%2C%20shares%20Robin%2C%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20years%20of%20being%20abused%2C%20girls%20start%20forming%20ideas%20in%20their%20head%20like%20I%E2%80%99m%20not%20capable%20of%20this%2C%20or%20I%20deserve%20to%20be%20treated%20like%20this.%20They%20feel%20that%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20the%20right%20to%20the%20good%20things.%20Watching%20these%20patterns%20change%20and%20overcoming%20these%20thoughts%20and%20misconceptions%20has%20been%20one%20of%20the%20most%20rewarding%20experiences%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Robin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20classes%2C%20every%20Krantikari%20has%20to%20do%20two%20extracurricular%20activities%20%E2%80%94%20one%20physical%20and%20one%20artistic%20%E2%80%94%20choosing%20from%20karate%2C%20music%2C%20dance%2C%20photography%2C%20drums%20and%20many%20more.%20The%20theatre%20also%20forms%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20every%20girl%E2%80%99s%20life%2C%20and%20they%20use%20this%20art%20form%20to%20share%20the%20story%20of%20sex%20workers%E2%80%99%20lives%20with%20people%20across%20the%20globe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKranti%E2%80%99s%20play%2C%20%E2%80%98Lal%20Batti%20Express%E2%80%99%2C%20has%20been%20performed%20across%20India%2C%20the%20US%20and%20the%20UK.%20The%20girls%20also%20travel%20and%20conduct%20workshops%20across%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-04-08-at-19.44.56-10-min-1713281617.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Theatre%20is%20a%20major%20focus%20area%20at%20Kranti%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-04-08-at-19.44.56-10-min-1713281617.jpeg%201600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-04-08-at-19.44.56-10-min-1713281617-300x199.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-04-08-at-19.44.56-10-min-1713281617-500x332.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-04-08-at-19.44.56-10-min-1713281617-768x510.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.th