.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20sent%20to%20live%20with%20my%20grandmother%20and%20that%20shift%2C%20in%20many%20ways%2C%20gave%20me%20the%20right%20set%20of%20opportunities%20to%20do%20what%20I%20always%20wanted%20to%20do.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20got%20admitted%20into%20a%20college%20in%20the%20Latur%20district%20but%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20afford%20the%20fees.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20principal%20at%20the%20time%20was%20a%20man%20of%20similar%20beliefs%20as%20mine.%20I%20used%20to%20tell%20him%20how%20I%20wanted%20to%20work%20for%20society.%20He%20secured%20a%20job%20as%20an%20errand%20boy%20for%20me%20in%20the%20college%20itself%20which%20helped%20me%20pay%20the%20fees%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20his%20vision%20that%20helped%20me%20connect%20with%20Baba%20Amte%2C%20the%20legendary%20social%20worker%20and%20activist%20who%20worked%20with%20people%20suffering%20from%20leprosy%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20principal%20sent%20me%20to%20him%2C%20seeking%20help%20for%20my%20vision.%20I%20used%20to%20go%20to%20his%20addresses%20and%20lectures%20to%20understand%20how%20one%20can%20help%20other%20people%20on%20a%20macro%20level.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Was%20called%20a%20fool%20behind%20my%20back%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20completing%20his%20graduation%2C%20he%20moved%20back%20to%20his%20village%20in%20Latur%20district%20to%20help%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F64071%2Fvellore-underprivileged-orphans-hope-house-college-education%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunderprivileged%20people%20gain%20employment.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20getting%20my%20hands%20dirty%20on%20the%20field%20but%20no%20one%20could%20understand%20what%20I%20was%20doing.%20I%20was%20the%20first%20one%20to%20graduate%2C%20they%20expected%20me%20to%20do%20some%20job.%20They%20could%20not%20understand%20why%20I%20would%20come%20back%20to%20the%20village.%20They%20considered%20me%20a%20failure%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDemotivated%20by%20all%20the%20comments%2C%20he%20moved%20to%20Pune.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20disheartened%20and%20lacked%20direction%20in%20my%20work.%20I%20moved%20to%20Pune%20seeking%20help%20from%20other%20social%20workers%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBaba%20Amte%20then%20suggested%20that%20he%20should%20first%20become%20financially%20independent%20and%20become%20a%20teacher.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20a%20school%20for%20the%20blind%20in%20front%20of%20my%20college%2C%20and%20once%20I%20completed%20my%20degree%2C%20I%20started%20to%20teach%20the%20kids%20there.%20It%20was%20there%20that%20I%20learnt%20that%20the%20kids%20get%20moved%20from%20one%20organisation%20to%20another%20constantly%2C%20either%20due%20to%20financial%20difficulties%20or%20lack%20of%20infrastructure.%20This%20hampered%20their%20growth%20and%20gave%20me%20the%20idea%20to%20do%20something%20to%20help%20people%20with%20visual%20impairments%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20this%20idea%20in%20mind%20of%20creating%20a%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3ESwadhar%20Kendra%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20in%20rural%20areas%20and%20villages%2C%20he%20left%20the%20city%20again.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20idea%20was%20that%20I%20wanted%20these%20children%20to%20get%20training%20and%20give%20them%20work%20opportunities%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20decided%20to%20leave%20the%20school%20and%20move%20back%20to%20the%20village%2C%20a%20student%20of%20his%20who%20also%20worked%20for%20him%2C%20decided%20to%20move%20too.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20could%20sing%20and%20dance%20well%2C%20and%20I%20used%20his%20art%20to%20grab%20the%20attention%20of%20the%20villagers.%20The%20%3Cem%3Esarpanch%20%3C%2Fem%3Etook%20us%20to%20the%20governor%20to%20get%20us%20a%20piece%20of%20land%20to%20stay%20and%20work%20on%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20the%20foundation%20stone%20of%20what%20later%20became%20Grameen%20Shramik%20Pratishthan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20got%20a%2040%C3%9740%20sq%20ft%20piece%20of%20land%20and%20we%20built%20a%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98jhopadi%E2%80%99%20%3C%2Fem%3E(hut).%20We%20would%20make%20bedsheets%20and%20blankets%20in%20the%20hut%20and%20then%20sell%20them.%20People%20were%20intrigued%20as%20to%20how%20a%20partially-impaired%20or%20blind%20person%20could%20do%20such%20a%20thing%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWord%20started%20spreading.%20Soon%2C%20more%20and%20more%20visually%20impaired%20people%20started%20to%20get%20in%20touch%20with%20him.%20%E2%80%9CI%20could%20finally%20see%20my%20dream%20shaping%20up.%20Soon%2C%20we%20were%20living%20with%20many%20more%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F99690%2Fgurugram-student-innovation-visually-impaired-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20visually%20impaired%20people%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fleather-13-1712585674.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20NGO%20helps%20people%20with%20disability%20find%20jobs.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fleather-13-1712585674.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fleather-13-1712585674-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fleather-13-1712585674-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fleather-13-1712585674-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fleather-13-1712585674-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-346857%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20NGO%20helps%20people%20with%20disability%20find%20jobs.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20all%20the%20activities%20came%20to%20a%20halt%20when%20the%20area%20was%20hit%20by%20heavy%20rains%20and%20a%20massive%20flood%3B%20everything%20was%20washed%20away.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20were%20too%20many%20people%20staying%20with%20me.%20We%20had%20lost%20all%20the%20huts%20that%20we%20had%20built%3B%20I%20had%20lost%20all%20hope.%20It%20was%20the%20people%20who%20encouraged%20me%20saying%20that%20bad%20times%20always%20pass%20away%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarishchandra%20went%20back%20to%20his%20native%20village%20Dangewadi%20and%20asked%20his%20father%20for%20help.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20some%20ancestral%20land%20and%20I%20asked%20my%20father%20for%20my%20share.%20Although%20I%20got%20a%20lot%20of%20retaliation%20from%20him%20as%20he%20believed%20that%20this%20was%20a%20waste%20of%20time%2C%20he%20gave%20me%20three-acre%20land%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarishchandra%20sold%20off%20that%20land%20and%20bought%20new%20land%20in%20Village%20Budhoda%20in%20the%20Ausa%20block%20of%20Latur%20district%2C%20which%20now%20holds%20the%20Grameen%20Shramik%20Pratishthan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20fighting%20the%20society%20and%20his%20family%20to%20start%20the%20organisation%2C%20Harishchandra%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20the%20first%20person%20to%20graduate%20from%20college.%20I%20could%20have%20just%20stuck%20to%20a%20job%20and%20%E2%80%98given%20back%E2%80%99%20to%20my%20family%2C%20but%20I%20wanted%20to%20use%20my%20education%20to%20give%20back%20to%20society.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFoundation%20of%20the%20NGO%20%26amp%3B%20how%20you%20can%20help%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarishchandra%20has%20spent%20decades%20of%20his%20life%20caring%20for%20the%20underserved.%20His%20son%20Prashant%20Sude%20is%20following%20in%20his%20father%E2%80%99s%20footsteps%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20father%20still%20works%20and%20stays%20every%20day%2C%20but%20I%20have%20now%20taken%20over%20the%20operations%20of%20the%20organisation.%20There%20are%20a%20few%20levels%20of%20interventions%20that%20we%20do%20to%20help%20people%20with%20disabilities%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NGO%20works%20to%20help%20people%20with%20disabilities%20by%20giving%20them%20training%20in%20different%20areas%20to%20help%20them%20become%20independent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUnder%20our%20Swadhar%20Scheme%2C%20what%20we%20initially%20did%20was%20train%20them%20in%20recycling%20old%20%3Cem%3Esarees%20%3C%2Fem%3Einto%20mats.%20The%20disposal%20of%20old%20%3Cem%3Esarees%20%3C%2Fem%3Eis%20a%20significant%20issue%2C%20contributing%20to%20environmental%20harm.%20At%20our%20hand-me-down%20centre%2C%20we%20recycle%20these%20sarees%20into%20mats%2C%20providing%20a%20sustainable%20solution%20to%20this%20problem.%20In%20doing%20so%2C%20they%20not%20only%20earn%20a%20livelihood%20but%20also%20contribute%20to%20addressing%20the%20environmental%20challenges%20associated%20with%20non-biodegradable%20waste%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20with%20changing%20times%2C%20Prashant%20realised%20that%20this%20training%20might%20not%20be%20viable%20after%20a%20few%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20to%20keep%20changing%20with%20time.%20I%20realised%20that%20this%20might%20not%20be%20a%20very%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F294290%2Fcouple-shares-personal-finance-tips-for-relationships-smart-money-management-tips%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efinancially%20smart%20occupation%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20future.%20In%202010%2C%20we%20started%20giving%20acupressure%20and%20massage%20training%20to%20visually%20impaired%20people.%20Massage%20is%20an%20excellent%20livelihood%20activity%20for%20visually%20challenged%20individuals%20because%20they%20possess%20sharp%20sensory%20abilities%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20training%20methods%20are%20simple%20yet%20effective%2C%20allowing%20both%20less-educated%20and%20well-educated%20individuals%20to%20learn%20acupressure%20massage%20systematically%20and%20scientifically.%20%E2%80%9CThrough%20our%20course%2C%20students%20learn%20anatomy%2C%20physiology%2C%20and%20various%20massage%20techniques%20practically.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20they%20become%20experts%20in%20the%20field%20of%20acupressure%20massage%20techniques%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20individuals%20are%20trained%2C%20they%20can%20return%20to%20their%20native%20village%20and%20practise%20there%20or%20stay%20at%20the%20centre%20and%20earn%20at%20least%20Rs%20500%20per%20massage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NGO%20also%20helps%20persons%20with%20disabilities%20get%20married%20and%20start%20a%20home.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20way%20society%20looks%20at%20people%20with%20disabilities%2C%20especially%20women%2C%20in%20villages%20and%20small%20towns%2C%20is%20concerning.%20If%20an%20individual%20wants%20to%20get%20married%20to%20someone%2C%20we%20take%20their%20responsibility%20and%20help%20them%20with%20all%20the%20arrangements%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20they%20have%20facilitated%20over%2050%20marriages%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fleather-12-1712585541.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Harishchandra%20Sude's%20son%20Prashant%20who%20now%20takes%20care%20of%20the%20operations.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fleather-12-1712585541.jpg%201200w%2C%2