is%20on%20practical%20skills%2C%20where%20students%20learn%20to%20use%20software%20like%20Canva%2C%20CorelDraw%2C%20and%20other%20tools%20to%20create%20designs%2C%20edit%20photos%2C%20and%20produce%20digital%20content.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COver%20the%20past%20two%20years%2C%20we%20have%20trained%2080%20visually%20challenged%20individuals%20in%20these%20digital%20skills%2C%20providing%20them%20with%20opportunities%20for%20meaningful%20employment%20and%20empowerment.%20They%20use%20the%20labs%20at%20the%20NGO%20to%20practise%20their%20skill%20and%20do%20their%20work%20without%20having%20to%20move%20a%20lot%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Prashant%20and%20Harishchandra%20along%20with%20many%20volunteers%20have%20helped%20hundreds%20of%20people%2C%20Prashant%20now%20wishes%20to%20expand%20the%20model%20throughout%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20visually%20impaired%20in%20our%20country%20are%20treated%20as%20second-class%20citizens.%20They%20are%20equally%20skilled%20if%20given%20the%20right%20set%20of%20opportunities%2C%20but%20they%20are%20neglected%20often%20by%20their%20own%20family.%20With%20Swadhaar%2C%20we%20are%20aiming%20to%20reduce%20this%20gap%20by%20presenting%20them%20with%20the%20right%20opportunities.%20We%20want%20to%20help%20them%20become%20independent%2C%20self-sustaining%2C%20and%20live%20the%20life%20they%20deserve%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Prashant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHarishchandra%20and%20Prashant%E2%80%99s%20fight%20to%20give%20equal%20rights%20to%20people%20with%20disabilities%20does%20not%20have%20to%20be%20theirs%20alone.%20You%20can%20contribute%20to%20their%20cause%20too.%20Click%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpages.razorpay.com%2Fpl_F40P3oSEKNjVkq%2Fview%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ehere%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20to%20do%20your%20part.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%20and%20Pranita%20Bhat)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(All%20pictures