ning%20and%20get%20a%20hands-on%20approach%20to%20social%20entrepreneurship.%20This%20is%20followed%20by%20a%20mock%20dive%20into%20the%20real%20world%20of%20business%20where%20participants%E2%80%99%20public%20skills%20are%20polished.%20They%20are%20also%20helped%20with%20fundraising%20and%20pitch-making%20along%20with%20a%20concrete%20budget%20plan%20for%20the%20first%20six%20months%20of%20running%20the%20NGO.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20kanthari%20course%20starts%20this%20April%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECredit%20Sabriye%20for%20designing%20such%20a%20holistic%20model%20and%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CSocial%20entrepreneurship%20is%20only%20one%20of%20many%20ways%20to%20make%20it%20a%20better%20world%2C%20right%3F%E2%80%9D%20I%20agree.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Use%20limitations%20as%20your%20springboard%E2%80%99%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fkanthari-4-1711980336.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Students%20at%20Braille%20Without%20Borders%20are%20encouraged%20to%20take%20part%20in%20vocational%20activities%20such%20as%20cheese%20making%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fkanthari-4-1711980336.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fkanthari-4-1711980336-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fkanthari-4-1711980336-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fkanthari-4-1711980336-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fkanthari-4-1711980336-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-346188%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22w